Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:15.42,Default,,0,0,40,,{\fs22\c&H000000}逍 遥 法 外 / 猫 鼠 游 戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢\N{\ren}Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎各位来到《真真假假》\N{\ren}and welcome to To Tell the Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的第一位客人  他让自己成为\N{\ren}Our first guest, he's made a career
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,最无耻的以冒名顶替为生的骗子\N{\ren}out of being the most outrageous impostor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们这个节目从未邀请过的\N{\ren}that we've ever come across on this show
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你很快就会明白我的意思的\N{\ren}and you're going to see what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,1号选手  请问你叫什么名字?\N{\ren}Number One what is your name, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫弗兰克·威廉·阿巴戈内尔\N{\ren}My name is Frank William Abagnale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,2号选手呢?\N{\ren}Number Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫弗兰克·威廉·阿巴戈内尔\N{\ren}My name is Frank William Abagnale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,3号选手呢?\N{\ren}Number Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫弗兰克·威廉·阿巴戈内尔\N{\ren}My name is Frank William Abagnale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,从1964年到1967年...\N{\ren}"From 1964 to 1967
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我成功地冒充了  泛美航空公司的 飞行员\N{\ren}"I successfully impersonated "an airline pilot for Pan Am Airways
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,免费飞了3百多万公里\N{\ren}"and I flew over two million miles for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那段时间  我是乔治亚州一家医院的\N{\ren}"During that time, I was also the chief resident pediatrician
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,儿科见习医生主管\N{\ren}"at a Georgia hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还是路易斯安那州首席检察官的一名助理\N{\ren}"and an assistant attorney general "for the state of Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在我被逮捕时   我被认为是\N{\ren}"By the time I was caught, I was considered
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,美国历史上  最年轻及最胆大的骗子\N{\ren}"the youngest and most daring con man in U.s. history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:04:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我在美国境外的26个国家  和境内的50个州里...\N{\ren}"I had cashed almost $4 million in fraudulent checks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,用伪造的支票套取了约4百万美元的现金\N{\ren}"in 26 foreign countries and all 50 states.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,而所有这些都是在我19岁生日之前做的\N{\ren}"And I did it all before my 19th birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫弗兰克·威廉·阿巴戈内尔\N{\ren}My name is Frank William Abagnale."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他要讲真话了\N{\ren}So, for the first time he's gonna have to tell the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,首先由基蒂发问\N{\ren}and we're going to start our questioning with Kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  1号选手  凭你的聪明才智\N{\ren}Thank you. Number One, why, with all your talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定是个非常聪明的家伙\N{\ren}and you're obviously a very bright fellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不找个合法的职业谋生?\N{\ren}why didn't you go in for a legitimate profession?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个挣钱多少的问题\N{\ren}It was really a question of dollars and cents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻的时候的时候  我需要钱...\N{\ren}When I was a young man, I needed the money
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这个职业  是最简单的挣钱方法\N{\ren}and I thought this list of careers was the easiest way to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\ren}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,2号选手  我发现这真奇妙\N{\ren}Number Two, I find this all very fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁最后抓住你的?\N{\ren}Who was it that finally caught you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫卡尔·汉莱提\N{\ren}His name was Carl Handratty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,汉-莱-提\N{\ren}Han-an-an-ratty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,莱提\N{\ren}Ratty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,汉莱提\N{\ren}Handratty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,汉莱提\N{\ren}Han-ratty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔·汉莱提\N{\ren}Carl Handratty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的  - 我...\N{\ren}-Yes. -I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,叫...卡尔·汉莱提\N{\ren}am... Carl Handratty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我代表美国的联邦调查局\N{\ren}I represent the FBI from the United states of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我有官方许可\N{\ren}Yeah. I have orders
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,来见那个美国囚犯  阿巴戈内尔\N{\ren}to see the American prisoner, Abagnale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}法国  马赛  1969年圣诞节前夕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你坐在这里\N{\ren}You sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不许开这扇门\N{\ren}You do not open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不许从这个小孔\N{\ren}You do not pass him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,递给他任何东西  \N{\ren}anything through the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\ren}Aw... Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我自己也有点感冒了\N{\ren}You know, I've got a little bit of a cold myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克\N{\ren}Frank...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,按照欧洲人权法...\N{\ren}I'm here to read the articles of extradition...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我来宣读引渡条例\N{\ren}according to the European Court for Human Rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,第1款: 引渡将被批准...\N{\ren}Article One: Extradition shall be granted
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,关于犯下按照法律应受惩罚罪行...\N{\ren}in respect of offenses punishable under the laws..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 救我  - 最长期限至少一年的\N{\ren}- help me. - for the maximum period of at least one year
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,严厉刑法\N{\ren}of a severe penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,救我\N{\ren}Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克...  住口\N{\ren}Frank... stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,救我\N{\ren}Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你没想骗我  是吧?\N{\ren}You don't think actually you can fool me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,还有16页没读完呢  注意听\N{\ren}16 pages to go. stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,第2款:\N{\ren}Article Two:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"如果引渡请求中  包含了几种不同的罪名...\N{\ren}"If the request for extradition "includes several separate offenses
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,而其中的每一项都可以进行判罪..."\N{\ren}each of which is punishable under the laws..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"根据 请求方的法律..."\N{\ren}"of the requesting party..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克?\N{\ren}Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克?\N{\ren}Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的!\N{\ren}Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,快找医生来!\N{\ren}Get me a doctor in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我需要名医生!  - 是的\N{\ren}- I need a doctor! -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,医生!  现在就要!\N{\ren}Doctor! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,别紧张  弗兰克  我们带你去医生那儿\N{\ren}Don't sweat it, Frank. We're going to get you right to a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  如果你能听见我  别担心\N{\ren}Frank, if you can hear me, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天早晨就带你回美国\N{\ren}I'm going to take you home in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,明天早晨  弗兰克\N{\ren}Home in the morning, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在做什么?  - 洗掉虱子\N{\ren}- What are you doing? - Washing off the lice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要尽快送这个人上飞机  他需要医生\N{\ren}This man has to be on a plane for America. He has to see a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,医生明天来\N{\ren}The doctor comes in tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我花那么大的功夫才抓住他\N{\ren}I have worked too long, too hard
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不是为了让你胡来\N{\ren}for you to take this away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他死了  你负责\N{\ren}If he dies, I'm holding you responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\N{\ren}Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克\N{\ren}Ah, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  卡尔...\N{\ren}Okay, Carl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回美国吧\N{\ren}let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,新罗谢尔·罗特瑞俱乐部...\N{\ren}The New Rochelle Rotary Club
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,的历史可以追述到1919\N{\ren}has a history that goes back to 1919.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在这些年中...\N{\ren}In all those years
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只有少数几位先生\N{\ren}we've only seen a handful of deserving gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,被荣幸接纳为终身会员\N{\ren}inducted as lifetime members.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一种荣誉\N{\ren}It's an honor that, uh
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,现已有57个名字铭记在这荣誉之墙上了\N{\ren}that has seen 57 names enshrined on the wall of honor
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚  我们会产生第58位\N{\ren}and tonight, we make it 58:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,请起立  让我来介绍我的好朋友\N{\ren}so please stand as I present my very good friend
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一个总是把我们的铅笔磨尖...\N{\ren}a man who keeps our pencils sharp...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把我们的钢笔充满墨水的人\N{\ren}and our pens in ink...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克·威廉·阿巴戈内尔\N{\ren}Frank William Abagnale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我很谦卑的站在\N{\ren}I stand here humbled
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特·瓦格纳市长...\N{\ren}by the presence of Mayor Robert Wagner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,及我们的俱乐部主席杰克·巴恩斯的旁边\N{\ren}and our club president, Jack Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,最想说的就是 我荣幸地看见我的太太保拉...\N{\ren}Most of all, I'm honored to see my loving wife Paula...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,和我的儿子小弗兰克...\N{\ren}and my son, Frank Jr...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克...  站起来  快点...\N{\ren}Frank... Aw, stand up. Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他坐在第一排\N{\ren}sitting in the front row.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,两只小老鼠掉进了一桶奶油中\N{\ren}Two little mice fell in a bucket of cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,第一只很快就放弃了  然后被淹死了\N{\ren}The first mouse quickly gave up and drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,第二只...  没有放弃.\N{\ren}The second mouse... wouldn't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他努力的挣扎着...\N{\ren}He struggled so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,最终他竟把奶油搅混成了黄油\N{\ren}that eventually he churned that cream into butter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,然后爬了出来\N{\ren}and crawled out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们  此刻  我就是那第二只老鼠\N{\ren}Gentlemen, as of this moment, I am that second mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你跳舞跳得比你爸还好  弗兰克\N{\ren}You're a better dancer than your father, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你听到了吗  爸爸?  - 开玩笑\N{\ren}- You hear that, Daddy? - Like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩们不知道她们这是为了什么\N{\ren}The girls don't know what they're in for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,给他展示一下我们见面时你跳舞的样子\N{\ren}show him the dance you were doing when we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谁能记得住?\N{\ren}Ah, who can remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那个法国小村庄的人\N{\ren}The people in that little French village
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,非常高兴见到美国人\N{\ren}were so happy to see Americans
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们决定给我们表演一场\N{\ren}they decided to put on a show for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以挤进来200个士兵  - 我们知道那个故事\N{\ren}- so they crammed 200 soldiers... - Yeah, we know the story, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,挤到那个小活动厅里\N{\ren}into that tiny social hall
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,而第一个上台的\N{\ren}and the first person to walk onstage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你母亲  她开始跳舞\N{\ren}is your mother, and she starts to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我们当时有几个月没见过女人了\N{\ren}You know, it had been months since we'd even seen a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,而这有位金发天使\N{\ren}and here's this blonde angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,金发美人\N{\ren}Blonde bombshell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那些男人都摒住了呼吸\N{\ren}And the men are literally holding their breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为你摒住了呼吸  你听见了吗?\N{\ren}Holding their breath for you. You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我转过去对我的朋友们说...\N{\ren}And I turned to my buddies and I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"不得到她我决不离开法国"\N{\ren}"I will not leave France without her."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而我真没离开\N{\ren}And I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你没离开\N{\ren}You didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我没离开\N{\ren}I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的  地毯\N{\ren}Oh, shit! Oh, shit, the rug!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,妈...\N{\ren}Aw, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信我做的\N{\ren}I can't believe I did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  没关系\N{\ren}No, no, it's nothing. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰基  快去找毛巾\N{\ren}Oh, Frankie, Frankie, get a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 保拉  没事的  - 好  好\N{\ren}- Paula... Come on. - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,和我跳支舞  保拉\N{\ren}Dance with me, Paula.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,无论什么时候跟你跳舞  我都会惹麻烦\N{\ren}Whenever I dance for you i get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,看这\N{\ren}Watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克!  醒醒  快点  要走了\N{\ren}Frank! Wake up. Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.96,0:12:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,快点  快点起来\N{\ren}Get up. Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  醒醒\N{\ren}Frank, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸\N{\ren}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天不用去上学  没关系\N{\ren}You don't have to go to school today. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?  下雪了吗?\N{\ren}Why? Is it snowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:12:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有黑色礼服?\N{\ren}Do you have a black suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我又睡过头了\N{\ren}I overslept again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要到城里去参加一个重要会议\N{\ren}We have a very important meeting in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了它  快点  快点\N{\ren}Eat that. Come on, come on, eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人  开门\N{\ren}Ma'am, open up. Just open up please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很重要  - 什么?\N{\ren}- It's important. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还有半个小时才开门\N{\ren}We don't open for half an hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,请把门打开  很重要的事\N{\ren}Open the door, please. Just open the door. It's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  我们还得过半小时开门\N{\ren}I-I'm sorry, we don't open for half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字  夫人?\N{\ren}What's your name, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,达茜\N{\ren}Darcy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,达茜  是个好听的名字\N{\ren}Darcy. That's a pretty name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点困难  我需要给我的孩子租套衣服\N{\ren}I'm in a bit of a fix. I need a suit for my kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我儿子弗兰克\N{\ren}This is my son Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他需要一套黑礼服  - 黑礼服\N{\ren}- He needs a black suit. - Black suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我家里有人死了\N{\ren}There was a death in the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父亲  85岁  战争英雄\N{\ren}My father, 85 years old, war hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?\N{\ren}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,下午要举行葬礼  军式葬礼...\N{\ren}There's a funeral this afternoon, military funeral
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,飞机头上飞  21响礼炮\N{\ren}planes flying overhead, 21-gun salute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克需要租套衣服用几个小时\N{\ren}Frank needs to borrow a suit for a couple of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  我们不出租衣服  也还没开门\N{\ren}I'm sorry, we don't loan suits, and we're not open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,达茜  求你  帮帮忙\N{\ren}Darcy... Darcy, please. Come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,达茜  这是你的吗?\N{\ren}Darcy... is this yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才在停车场发现的\N{\ren}I just found it in the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是从你的脖子上滑落的\N{\ren}It must've slipped right off your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,别撞到路牙\N{\ren}Don't hit the curb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,现在下车  从后边绕过来给我开门\N{\ren}Now get out, walk around the back and hold the door open for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\ren}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 然后呢?  - 好  不要咧嘴笑\N{\ren}- What's next? - Okay, stop grinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我进去后  你回到车前座等我\N{\ren}When I get inside, you go back to the front seat and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,即使警察来开罚单\N{\ren}Even if a cop comes and writes you a ticket
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,也不要挪动车  明白吗?\N{\ren}you don't move the car, understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,爸  这都是为什么?\N{\ren}Dad, wha-what's all this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道为什么杨基队总是赢吗?\N{\ren}You know why the Yankees always win, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他们有米基·曼托?\N{\ren}'Cause they have Mickey Mantle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不  是因为其它队总盯着他们的条纹衣服看\N{\ren}No, it's 'cause the other teams can't stop staring at those damn pinstripes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧好了\N{\ren}Watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,美国大通银行的经理\N{\ren}The manager of Chase Manhattan Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要给你父亲开门了\N{\ren}is about to open the door for your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,阿巴戈内尔先生...\N{\ren}Mr. Abagnale, um
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们通常不会贷款给那些有税务问题的人\N{\ren}we don't usually loan money to people who have unresolved business with the IRs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个误会\N{\ren}That's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我用错了记账的人\N{\ren}I hired the wrong guy to do my books.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是个任何人都可能犯的错误\N{\ren}A mistake, I... anybody could make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我只需要你们帮助我渡过难关\N{\ren}I just need you guys to help me weather the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  你正因骗税问题被政府调查\N{\ren}sir, you're being investigated by the government for tax fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的商店在新罗谢尔很有名\N{\ren}My store is a landmark in New Rochelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我的客户遍布纽约\N{\ren}I have customers all over New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不是大通银行的客户\N{\ren}Well, you're not a customer at Chase Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不认识你\N{\ren}We don't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信新罗谢尔的银行认识你\N{\ren}I'm sure your bank in New Rochelle, they know you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.45,0:15:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能帮你摆脱困境  - 我的银行倒闭了\N{\ren}- they could help you out. - My bank went out of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,像你们这样的银行使它们倒闭的\N{\ren}Banks like this one put them out of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我犯了个错误  我承认这点\N{\ren}Now, I know I made a mistake, I admit that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但这些人想吸血\N{\ren}but these people want blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想要我的商店\N{\ren}They want my store.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至威胁过我说要把我投入监狱\N{\ren}They've threatened to put me in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这是美国  对吗?  我不是罪犯\N{\ren}This is America, right? I'm not a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是新罗谢尔旋转俱乐部终身会员  \N{\ren}I'm a Medal of Honor winner a lifetime member
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,荣誉奖章获得者\N{\ren}of the New Rochelle Rotary Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我想求你做的就是帮我打败这些家伙\N{\ren}All I'm asking is for you to help me beat these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是输赢问题  而是风险问题\N{\ren}It's not a question of winning and losing. It's a question of risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是世界上最大的银行\N{\ren}You're the largest bank in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哪来...\N{\ren}Where's the fu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里... 哪里有风险?\N{\ren}Whe... Where's the risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,爸  你怎么能让他们像那样拿走我们的车?\N{\ren}Dad, how could you just let him take our car like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他多付了500美元  所以是我们拿了他的\N{\ren}He didn't take anything. We took him. He overpaid by $500.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,得了  弗兰克\N{\ren}Come on, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去还衣服吧\N{\ren}Let's return the suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那地方不错\N{\ren}This place is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是小了些  但不用操那么多心\N{\ren}It's small but, you know it's going to be a lot less work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,家务活少多了\N{\ren}A lot less work for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸\N{\ren}Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你母亲呢?\N{\ren}Where's your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\ren}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,她说什么要去找工作\N{\ren}she said something about going to look for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她能做什么\N{\ren}What's she gonna be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在蜈蚣农场卖鞋?\N{\ren}a shoe salesman at a centipede farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么?\N{\ren}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要点薄饼吗?\N{\ren}You want some pancakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在我儿子16岁生日这天  晚餐吃博饼?\N{\ren}For dinner? On my son's 16th birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才不吃薄饼\N{\ren}We're not gonna eat pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么那样看着我?  你以为我忘了?\N{\ren}Come on, why are you looking at me like that? You thought I forgot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我没以为你忘了  - 我以你的名义\N{\ren}-I didn't think you forgot. -I opened a checking account
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,开了个支票账户\N{\ren}in your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,账户里存了25美元  随便你买什么\N{\ren}I put $25 in the account so you can buy whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别告诉你母亲  - 我不会的\N{\ren}- Don't tell your mother. - I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢你  爸爸\N{\ren}Thanks, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.72,0:17:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那家银行不是拒绝给你贷款了吗?\N{\ren}Didn't that bank turn you down for a loan, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  他们都拒绝我了\N{\ren}Yes, they all turned me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那怎么还在那儿开户?\N{\ren}Then why you opening a banking account with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为迟早你会用到银行\N{\ren}Well, because one day, you'll want something from these people
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,贷款买房子  买车\N{\ren}a house, a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他们控制这些钱\N{\ren}They have all the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这有50张支票  弗兰克...\N{\ren}There's 50 checks there, Frank
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说  从今天开始...\N{\ren}which means, from this day on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你就加入了他们的小俱乐部\N{\ren}you're in their little club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.98,0:18:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我加入了他们的小俱乐部\N{\ren}I'm in their little club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有了支票  就有了一切\N{\ren}You got that, you got it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,上边甚至有我的名字\N{\ren}It's even got my name there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一步登天\N{\ren}To the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一步登天  - 一步登天\N{\ren}-To the moon! -To the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了吗?  那只不过是所学校\N{\ren}see that? It's just a school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,和西波恩中学没什么两样\N{\ren}No different than Westbourne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,妈  你说过要戒烟的\N{\ren}Ma... you said you were going to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克   在这儿你不用穿校服\N{\ren}Frankie, you don't have to wear the uniform here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不脱了你的上衣呢?\N{\ren}Why don't you take off your jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我习惯了\N{\ren}I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\ren}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事?\N{\ren}Oh, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道上法语课的17号教室在哪?\N{\ren}Do you know where room 17 French is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,知道  在...\N{\ren}Yeah, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你竟杀了他\N{\ren}But you frickin' killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你在卖百科全书吗?\N{\ren}You selling encyclopedias?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他看上去像位代课老师\N{\ren}Yeah, he looks like a substitute teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,安静  各位!\N{\ren}Quiet down, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫阿巴戈内尔先生!\N{\ren}My name is Mr. Abagnale!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是阿巴戈内尔  不是阿巴戈诺勒...\N{\ren}That's Abagnale, not Abagnahlee
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:20:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是阿巴戈内勒  而是阿巴戈内尔\N{\ren}not Abagnaylee, but Abagnale!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  请哪位来告诉我上次讲到哪里了\N{\ren}Now, somebody please tell me where you left off in your textbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  如果我需要再说一遍的话\N{\ren}Excuse me, people, if I need to ask again
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要告你们全班的状\N{\ren}I'm going to write up the entire class.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下!\N{\ren}Take your seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,第7章\N{\ren}Chapter seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,请打开书到第8章...\N{\ren}Will you please open your textbooks to, uh, chapter eight
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开始吧\N{\ren}and we'll get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  你叫什么?\N{\ren}Excuse me, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.61,0:20:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,布拉德\N{\ren}Brad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,布拉德  你为什么不站到教室前面\N{\ren}Brad, why don't you get up here in front of the class here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,朗读第5段对话\N{\ren}and read conversation number five?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,法国\N{\ren}"Les Francais sonts
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,呃  一般\N{\ren}uh, generalement
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在他们的国家\N{\ren}dans leur pais que...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎每个人都有这样的感觉\N{\ren}presque tout le monde a cette impression..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们派我来的\N{\ren}They sent for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说他们需要给罗伯塔找个代课老师\N{\ren}They said they needed a sub for Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我老远从狄克逊赶来\N{\ren}I came all the way from-from Dixon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我总是给罗伯塔代课\N{\ren}Well, uh, I always sub for Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不读了?\N{\ren}Excuse me, why aren't you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也不来贝拉明杰斐逊中学代课了!\N{\ren}I'll never come back to-to Bellarmine Jefferson again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉他们别给我打电话\N{\ren}You tell them not to call me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们认为像我这样一把年纪的妇女...\N{\ren}What do they think, it's easy for a woman my age
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还花了我那么多路费容易吗?\N{\ren}and all the money that it costs to travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会给我报销的\N{\ren}I tell you, they don't give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,阿巴内尔先生和夫人\N{\ren}Mr. And Mrs. Abagnale
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这个问题不是关于你儿子出勤率的\N{\ren}this is not a question of your son's attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉的告诉你们  在过去的一周中\N{\ren}I regret to inform you that for the past week
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克替格拉瑟夫人教授了法语课\N{\ren}Frank has been teaching Mrs. Glasser's French class.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他干什么了?\N{\ren}He what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的儿子假装成代课老师\N{\ren}Your son has been pretending to be a substitute teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,给学生们讲课  布置作业...\N{\ren}lecturing the students, uh, giving out homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.01,0:21:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,格拉瑟太太病了  \N{\ren}Mrs. Glasser has been ill...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而代课老师又无法上课\N{\ren}and there was some confusion with the real sub.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天你们的儿子开了个家长会...\N{\ren}Your son held a teacher-parent conference yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,准备安排到特伦顿的一家法国面包厂实习\N{\ren}and was planning a class field trip to a French bread factory in Trenton.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你们明白了问题所在吗?\N{\ren}Do you see the problem we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 达文波特小姐?  - 是的\N{\ren}- Mrs. Davenport? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个假条  不能上第5-6节课\N{\ren}Uh, I have a note to miss fifth and sixth period today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:21:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跟医生有个约会  - 稍等一下\N{\ren}- Doctor's appointment. - One moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上回来\N{\ren}I'll be right with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么?  - 你应该把它折起来\N{\ren}- Yes? - You should fold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么?\N{\ren}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那个假条  是假的  对吗?\N{\ren}That note. It's a fake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该折起来\N{\ren}You should fold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是我妈妈写的假条  我跟医生有预约\N{\ren}It's... It's a note from my mom. I have a doctor's appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对  但纸没有折痕\N{\ren}Yeah, but there's no crease in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈递给你假条时...\N{\ren}When your mom hands you a note to miss school
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一般是先折起来  再放进口袋里\N{\ren}the first thing you do is, you fold it and you put it in your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是真的  折痕在哪里?\N{\ren}I mean, if it's real, where's the crease?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.19,0:22:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克\N{\ren}Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.36,0:22:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,妈  我回来了\N{\ren}Ma, I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:22:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得我和你说过的?\N{\ren}Oh, you remember that girl Joanna
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:22:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女孩乔安娜吗?\N{\ren}I was telling you about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我跟她约会了\N{\ren}I asked her out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.70,0:23:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们要去参加3年级舞会\N{\ren}Think we're going to go to the Junior Prom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,妈  这是我的驾驶执照吗?\N{\ren}Ma, is this my driver's license?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这些  2间卧室\N{\ren}That's all there is, two bedrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.85,0:23:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克\N{\ren}Oh, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得爸爸的朋友吗?\N{\ren}You remember Dad's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.77,0:23:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克·巴恩斯\N{\ren}Jack Barnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,俱乐部的\N{\ren}From the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好  - 他路过这里来看看你父亲\N{\ren}- Hello. - He came by looking for your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我带他看了房子\N{\ren}I was giving him a tour of the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很宽敞  保拉\N{\ren}It's very, uh, uh, spacious, Paula.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸在商店\N{\ren}Dad's at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.69,0:23:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  你长得越来越像你父亲了\N{\ren}so, Frank... you're getting to look more like your old man every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.60,0:23:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的三明治  保拉\N{\ren}Thanks for the sandwich, Paula.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.00,0:23:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再见  - 等一下\N{\ren}- I'll see you later, eh? - Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.32,0:23:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的吗?\N{\ren}Is this yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:23:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  弗兰克\N{\ren}Well, thanks, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:24:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是主席别针\N{\ren}Uh, that's the President's pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是丢了它  麻烦可就大了\N{\ren}I'd be in deep trouble if I lost that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.85,0:24:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\ren}I'll see you all later, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你饿吗  弗兰克?\N{\ren}Are you hungry, Frankie?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.61,0:24:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你做三明治\N{\ren}I'll make you a sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.85,0:24:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克想跟你父亲谈生意\N{\ren}Jack wanted to talk business with your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.32,0:24:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他觉得我们应该找个律师控告政府\N{\ren}He thinks we should get a lawyer and sue the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.71,0:24:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他们对我们做的不合法\N{\ren}That is not legal what they're doing to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.61,0:24:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么不说话?\N{\ren}Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.16,0:25:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会告诉他的  是吗?\N{\ren}You're not going to tell him... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.89,0:25:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不会\N{\ren}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.68,0:25:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那就对了\N{\ren}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.02,0:25:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么可说的\N{\ren}There's nothing to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.55,0:25:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我要出去几个小时\N{\ren}I'm going out for a few hours
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.51,0:25:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,拜访一些网球俱乐部的朋友\N{\ren}to visit some old friends from the tennis club and...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.69,0:25:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我回家后  我们一起吃晚饭\N{\ren}when I get home, we'll all have dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.00,0:25:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗?\N{\ren}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.19,0:25:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么也不会说\N{\ren}But you won't say anything
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.43,0:25:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那样太傻...   对吗?\N{\ren}because it's... it's just silly, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.60,0:25:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怎么控告政府?\N{\ren}How could we sue anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.30,0:25:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要点钱吗  弗兰克?\N{\ren}Oh... do you need some money, Frankie?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.20,0:25:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,拿几美元去买些唱片?\N{\ren}A few dollars to buy some record albums?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.68,0:25:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,给你5块钱\N{\ren}Here, take five dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.59,0:25:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,或者10块\N{\ren}Or-Or ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.44,0:25:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你答应过要戒掉的\N{\ren}You promised you were going to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.22,0:26:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,妈  我回来了\N{\ren}Ma, I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.69,0:26:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你离我远点  听见了吗?\N{\ren}You... You stay away from me, hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.92,0:26:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你离我远点  我不知道你是谁\N{\ren}You stay away from me... I don't know who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.16,0:26:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你回来...\N{\ren}but if you ever come back here again...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.18,0:26:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  冷静点  好吗?\N{\ren}Frankie! Frank, Frank, calm down, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.69,0:26:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫迪克·科斯纳\N{\ren}I'm Dick Kesner.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.80,0:26:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你把东西放这\N{\ren}Now, I want you to leave your things here
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.59,0:26:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我进另一间屋\N{\ren}and follow me into the next room, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.66,0:26:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都在等你\N{\ren}They're all waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.78,0:26:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必害怕\N{\ren}You don't have to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.38,0:26:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这里  弗兰克  我一直在这里\N{\ren}I'm right here, Frank. I'll always be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.47,0:26:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有法律\N{\ren}But there are laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.09,0:26:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这个国家的每一件事 都要合法\N{\ren}Everything in this country has to be legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.54,0:26:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们要做些决定\N{\ren}so what we need to do is make some decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.73,0:26:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯纳先生就是为这个来的\N{\ren}That's what Mr. Kesner is here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.43,0:27:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很多时候这些决定是由法庭来做的\N{\ren}Many times these decisions are left up to the courts
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.80,0:27:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但可能会很贵  弗兰克\N{\ren}but that can be very expensive, Frank
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.07,0:27:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 人们为了孩子而打架  - 没人在打架\N{\ren}- people fighting over their children. - Nobody is fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.39,0:27:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我  弗兰克  没人在打架\N{\ren}Look at me, Frank. Nobody is fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.66,0:27:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,爸  到底怎么了?\N{\ren}Dad, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.24,0:27:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爸  到底怎么了?\N{\ren}Dad, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.88,0:27:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得你的祖母夏娃吗?\N{\ren}Do you remember your grandma, Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.39,0:27:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她今天早晨到的\N{\ren}she arrived this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.10,0:27:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\ren}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.81,0:27:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白我们在跟你讲什么吗  弗兰克?\N{\ren}Do you understand what we're saying to you, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.73,0:27:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你父亲要离婚了\N{\ren}Your father and I are getting a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.37,0:27:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都不会改变\N{\ren}Nothing's gonna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.82,0:27:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还可以见面\N{\ren}We're still gonna see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.37,0:27:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了  求你  不要打断\N{\ren}stop it, please, Frank. Don't interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.36,0:27:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必读完这些\N{\ren}Frank, you don't have to read all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.03,0:27:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,多数都是关于你父母的  成年人间烦人的事情\N{\ren}Most of it's for your parents... boring adult business...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.61,0:27:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但这段很重要...\N{\ren}but this paragraph right here, this is important
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.17,0:28:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它说的是离婚后你将跟谁在一起...\N{\ren}because it states who you're gonna live with...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.53,0:28:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,离婚后\N{\ren}after the divorce...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.30,0:28:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你受谁的监护\N{\ren}whose custody you will be in.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.54,0:28:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有个空白处\N{\ren}And there's a blank space right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.10,0:28:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你到厨房去  坐在桌前...\N{\ren}And I want you to go into the kitchen sit at the table
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.46,0:28:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,写上父亲或母亲的名字\N{\ren}and put a name down.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.00,0:28:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要着急\N{\ren}You can take as long as you want
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.12,0:28:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是当你回到这个房间时...\N{\ren}but when you come back into this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.30,0:28:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看见那条线上写好了名字\N{\ren}I want to see a name on that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.64,0:28:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  你只要写下个人名就行了\N{\ren}Frank, just write down a name and this will all be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.38,0:28:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不会有事的\N{\ren}It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.21,0:28:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,爸  什么名字?\N{\ren}Dad, what name?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.19,0:28:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你母亲或你父亲\N{\ren}Your mother or your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.39,0:28:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,把名字写在那里 就那么简单\N{\ren}Just put the name there. It's as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.15,0:28:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不要害怕\N{\ren}And don't look so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.50,0:28:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是考试\N{\ren}It's not a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.10,0:28:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不回答错\N{\ren}There's no wrong answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.95,0:28:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,请给1张到大中心的票\N{\ren}One ticket to Grand Central, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.96,0:28:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,3.50美元  先生\N{\ren}That'll be $3.50, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.22,0:28:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我付支票可以吗?\N{\ren}Is it okay if I write you a check?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.82,0:29:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔   我何时可以给父亲打电话?\N{\ren}Carl, when do I get to call my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.99,0:29:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,到纽约后你就可以打给他\N{\ren}You can call him when we get to New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.00,0:29:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}1969年  法国  巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.36,0:29:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们7个小时后到飞机场\N{\ren}We leave for the airport in seven hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.40,0:29:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别动  一直坐在那里\N{\ren}Until then, just sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.19,0:29:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,安静点\N{\ren}Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.81,0:29:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔  旅馆的另外一侧有\N{\ren}You know, Carl, on the other side of the hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.72,0:29:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,面对公园的套房\N{\ren}they got suites that face the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.04,0:29:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是联邦调查局能担负的最好的房间了\N{\ren}It's the best room the FBI can afford.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.81,0:29:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  我原来呆的地方更差\N{\ren}It's okay, I've stayed in worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.93,0:29:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,马德里克先生...\N{\ren}Mr. Mudrick...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.33,0:29:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,马德里克先生  求你  你得听我说\N{\ren}Mr. Mudrick, please. You have to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.68,0:29:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想听你解释\N{\ren}I don't want to hear your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.50,0:29:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,2张支票退回来了\N{\ren}This is two checks that bounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.32,0:29:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我有多大的麻烦吗?\N{\ren}You know how much trouble I'm in?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.14,0:29:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不  听我说  我告诉你  是银行  银行犯了一个错误\N{\ren}No, but listen, I'm telling you, the bank, they made the mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.59,0:29:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上再给你写张支票!\N{\ren}I'll write you another check right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.12,0:29:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我看上去像小孩子那么好骗吗?\N{\ren}What, do I look like I was born yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.65,0:29:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你看  现在是半夜\N{\ren}Look, it's midnight, Mr. Mudrick.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.21,0:29:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我能去哪?  - 你是个孩子  回家去\N{\ren}- Where am I gonna go? - You're a goddamn kid. Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.17,0:30:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你明白\N{\ren}I mean, I hope you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.47,0:30:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我的老板派我到 布鲁克林区  然后到皇后区\N{\ren}My boss sent me to Brooklyn, then Queens.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.34,0:30:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他想让我去长岛...\N{\ren}Now he wants me in Long Island
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.82,0:30:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,带些顾客来城里玩一晚上\N{\ren}to take a few clients out for a night on the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.65,0:30:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  我不能兑现其它银行的支票\N{\ren}I'm sorry, but we're not allowed to cash checks from other banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.96,0:30:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没法确认它们有效\N{\ren}How would we know if they were any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.27,0:30:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你叫什么名字来着?\N{\ren}What did you say your name was?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.06,0:30:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿什蕾  - 阿什蕾\N{\ren}- Ashley. - Ashley.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.42,0:30:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我在外边人行道上发现了什么\N{\ren}you know what I found on the sidewalk out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.95,0:31:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是从你脖子上滑落的\N{\ren}Must've slipped right off your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.68,0:31:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么需要我帮助吗  年轻人?\N{\ren}Is there something I can help you with, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.44,0:31:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,下星期是我祖母的生日\N{\ren}Well, you see, it's my grandmother's birthday next week
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.26,0:31:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我想送给她件什么特别的东西\N{\ren}and I want to get her something extra-special.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.97,0:31:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 我下星期考试  而书却丢了\N{\ren}Please, I mean it's my midterm next week and my books were stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.34,0:31:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了  只是5美元\N{\ren}Please, it's just five dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.85,0:31:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没人会知道的\N{\ren}No one would have to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.93,0:31:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  但我们不允许\N{\ren}I'm sorry, but we are not allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.05,0:31:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,收不认识的人的支票\N{\ren}to take checks from people we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.53,0:32:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到纽约  很高兴你回来了  机长\N{\ren}Pleasure to have you back, Captain Carlson.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.48,0:32:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样  安吉洛?\N{\ren}What do you think, Angelo?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.91,0:32:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,番茄今天下午熟了\N{\ren}The tomatoes are ripe this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.64,0:32:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么?\N{\ren}Well, what have we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.82,0:32:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能签个名吗? -肯定行\N{\ren}- Can I have your autograph? - ou betcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.90,0:32:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也能给我签名吗?  - 你将来当飞行员?\N{\ren}- Can I have your autograph, too? - You gonna be a pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.97,0:32:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好  签一个\N{\ren}All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.17,0:32:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,给你  在学校努力学啊.\N{\ren}There you go. Work hard in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.16,0:32:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的爸爸\N{\ren}Dear Dad:
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.59,0:32:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经决定去当飞行员\N{\ren}I have decided to become an airline pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.95,0:32:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经申请了所有的大航空公司\N{\ren}I have applied to all the big airlines
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.12,0:32:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有希望的面试已经排满日程了\N{\ren}and I have several promising interviews lined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.70,0:32:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈怎样?\N{\ren}How's Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.69,0:32:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你最近给她打电话了吗?\N{\ren}Have you called her lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.56,0:32:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,爱你的  儿子  弗兰克\N{\ren}Love, your son, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.64,0:32:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\ren}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.51,0:32:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我是穆偌中学的弗兰克·布莱克\N{\ren}I'm Frank Black from Murrow High school
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.87,0:33:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟摩根先生有个约会\N{\ren}and I have an appointment with Mr. Morgan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.53,0:33:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是给学校的报纸写文章的年轻人\N{\ren}You're the young man who's writing the article for the school paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.49,0:33:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对  是我  我想知道\N{\ren}Yes, ma'am, that's me. I want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.63,0:33:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,关于成为飞行员的每一件事\N{\ren}everything there is to know about being a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.35,0:33:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,泛美公司都飞哪些飞机场?\N{\ren}What airports does Pan Am fly to?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.24,0:33:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,飞行员1年收入多少?\N{\ren}What does a pilot make in a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.79,0:33:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谁告诉他们往哪儿飞?\N{\ren}And who tells them where they're gonna fly to?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.22,0:33:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,慢点  一个一个来\N{\ren}Whoa, whoa, whoa. Slow down. Just take 'em one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.88,0:33:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  这是什么意思...\N{\ren}All right. What does it mean
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.69,0:33:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,当一个飞行员问另一个飞行员:\N{\ren}when one pilot says to another pilot:
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.52,0:33:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"你装配了些什么?"\N{\ren}"What kind of equipment are you on?"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.08,0:33:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想知道你们使用什么样的飞机\N{\ren}They just want to know what kind of aircraft you're flying:
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.48,0:33:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是DC-8还是707  或者星座式\N{\ren}Is it a DC-8 707, Constellation?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.63,0:33:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那些我见过的飞行员戴的徽章是干什么的?\N{\ren}And what about those I.D. badges that I've seen pilots wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.81,0:33:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,每个飞行员有两样东西必须\N{\ren}Well, every pilot has to have two things with him
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.05,0:33:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,随身携带  一个是航空公司的职员徽章\N{\ren}at all times: One is his airline personnel badge...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.33,0:33:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就像泛美航空公司的这个\N{\ren}Looks just like this one here, from Pan Am...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.58,0:33:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个就是联邦航空局的执照\N{\ren}the other one is their FAA license...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.62,0:33:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这个一样\N{\ren}and that looks just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.61,0:33:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  我能复印1份这\N{\ren}Oh. Sir, do you think I can make a copy of this
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.27,0:33:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,贴在我的文章里吗?\N{\ren}to put into my article?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.55,0:33:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  你拿去吧  再有3年过期了\N{\ren}Oh, Frank, you can have that one. It's three years expired.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.51,0:33:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  还有你的身份徽章呢?\N{\ren}Aw, thanks! And what about your I.D. badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.97,0:33:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有没有一个多余的借给我?\N{\ren}You have an extra one I could borrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.34,0:33:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那个我帮不了你\N{\ren}Oh, no, I can't help you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.83,0:33:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要从宝丽来公司定制\N{\ren}Those are special-ordered from Polaroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.82,0:33:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一弄到它的办法\N{\ren}The only way to get one of those
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.64,0:34:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就是成为一名真的泛美公司的飞行员\N{\ren}is to become a real live pilot for Pan American Airways.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.80,0:34:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}泛美航空
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.91,0:34:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这是泛美公司  要我帮忙吗?\N{\ren}Pan Am, may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.56,0:34:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  你好  我打电话是为了一套制服\N{\ren}Yeah, hello. I'm calling about a uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.15,0:34:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等我转到采购部  - 谢谢\N{\ren}- Hold for Purchasing. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.24,0:34:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,采购部\N{\ren}Purchasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.38,0:34:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是一名来自旧金山基地的副驾驶员\N{\ren}Hi. I'm a copilot based out of san Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.32,0:34:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨晚飞到纽约\N{\ren}I flew a flight into New York last night
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.54,0:34:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但问题是  我三小时后要去巴黎  马上要出发\N{\ren}but the problem is... I'm headed out to, uh, Paris in three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.22,0:34:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要什么帮忙?\N{\ren}How can we help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.63,0:34:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我把我的制服送到酒店清洗\N{\ren}I sent my uniform to be cleaned through the hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.50,0:34:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但我想他们给弄丢了\N{\ren}and I... I guess they must have lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.15,0:34:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们丢了制服  这事经常发生\N{\ren}They lost a uniform. Happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.68,0:34:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,去百老汇街19号  好工制服公司\N{\ren}Go down to the Well-Built Uniform Company at Ninth and Broadway.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.58,0:34:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是我们的制服提供商\N{\ren}They're our uniform supplier.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.94,0:34:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉罗森先生你要去\N{\ren}I'll tell Mr. Rosen you're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.12,0:34:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你看上去当飞行员太年轻了\N{\ren}You look too young to be a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.10,0:34:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是副驾驶员\N{\ren}I'm a copilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.00,0:34:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这么紧张?\N{\ren}Why so nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.87,0:34:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你会有何感觉  如果你...\N{\ren}How would you feel if you, uh
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.78,0:34:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,第一周刚上班就把制服丢了?\N{\ren}Lost your uniform first week on the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.36,0:34:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,放松点\N{\ren}Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.33,0:34:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,泛美公司有的是制服\N{\ren}Pan Am's got lots of uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.92,0:34:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一共是164美元\N{\ren}It's gonna be $164.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.52,0:34:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  我给你写张支票\N{\ren}Great. I'II, uh, I'll write you a check.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.61,0:34:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  不收支票  不收现金\N{\ren}sorry, no checks, no cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.77,0:34:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你得写下你的职员身份号码\N{\ren}You'll have to fill in your employee I.D. number
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.97,0:35:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我向泛美公司收帐\N{\ren}and then I'll bill Pan Am.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.94,0:35:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,然后他们再从你下次薪水中扣除\N{\ren}They'll take it out of your next paycheck.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.12,0:35:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那更好\N{\ren}Even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.56,0:35:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的爸爸...\N{\ren}Dear Dad:
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.01,0:35:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是告诉我一个诚实的人  没什么可怕的\N{\ren}You always told me that an honest man has nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.02,0:35:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我尽量不去害怕\N{\ren}So I'm trying my best not to be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.59,0:35:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起我离家出走了  但你不用担心\N{\ren}I'm sorry I ran away, but you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.15,0:35:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在要把那些都找回来  爸爸\N{\ren}I'm gonna get it all back now, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.35,0:35:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证  我要都找回来\N{\ren}I promise. I'm going to get it all back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.07,0:35:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你是真的飞行员吗?\N{\ren}Are you a real live pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.18,0:35:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定是  小姐  你叫什么名字?\N{\ren}I sure am, little lady. What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.01,0:35:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 席琳  - 席琳  很高兴见到你\N{\ren}- Celine. - Celine, it's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.00,0:35:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很高兴见到你\N{\ren}It's a pleasure to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.09,0:35:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,50  70\N{\ren}That's fifty, seventy
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.92,0:35:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,80  90  100美元\N{\ren}eighty, ninety, one hundred dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.38,0:35:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你在巴黎过得愉快\N{\ren}You have yourself a great time in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.89,0:35:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我总是过得愉快\N{\ren}I always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.54,0:35:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰一下\N{\ren}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.58,0:36:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫约翰.摩迪治  我管理这家分行\N{\ren}I'm John Modiger. I manage this branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.13,0:36:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢你来到这里  使用我们的银行服务\N{\ren}I want to thank you for coming in and using our institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.23,0:36:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,幸会  约翰\N{\ren}Well, it's a pleasure to meet you, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.44,0:36:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我还会来的  - 好\N{\ren}- I'll be back again. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.27,0:36:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前住过我们酒店吗?\N{\ren}Have you stayed with us before?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.66,0:36:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我以前主要是在西海岸一带\N{\ren}Uh, no, I've been primarily based on the West Coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.05,0:36:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以给你写张支票付房钱吗?\N{\ren}Is it all right if I write you a check for the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.16,0:36:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没问题  先生  - 很好\N{\ren}- No problem, sir. - Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.49,0:36:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道  能否使用个人支票?\N{\ren}I was also wondering if I could write you a personal check?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.54,0:36:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对于航空公司的职员 我们最多兑现100美元个人支票\N{\ren}For airline personnel, we cash personal checks up to $100.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.09,0:36:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,薪水支票我们最多兑现300美元现金\N{\ren}Payroll checks we cash up to $300.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.51,0:36:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说工资支票给兑现300美元?\N{\ren}Did you say $300 for a payroll check?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.05,0:36:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的爸爸...\N{\ren}Dear Dad:
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.85,0:36:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经决定要成为泛美航空公司的飞行员了\N{\ren}I've decided to become a pilot for Pan American Airways...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.08,0:36:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,泛美是天空中最值得信任的名字\N{\ren}the most trusted name in the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.98,0:36:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经接受我参加他们的培训\N{\ren}They've accepted me into their training program
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.22,0:36:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,并说如果我努力工作\N{\ren}and told me that if I work hard
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.26,0:36:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不久我就真要插上翅膀了\N{\ren}I should earn my wings real soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.20,0:37:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,请跟10年级的乔安娜·卡尔顿联系\N{\ren}Please get in touch with Joanna Carlton from the tenth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.57,0:37:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他说我抱歉不能带她去3年级舞会\N{\ren}Tell her I'm sorry that I could not take her to the Junior Prom.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.57,0:37:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,爱你的  儿子  弗兰克\N{\ren}Love, your son, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.59,0:37:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好吗?  - 很好  谢谢\N{\ren}- Hello, how are you? - Fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.91,0:37:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我有1张薪水支票想兑现金\N{\ren}I have a payroll check here I'd like to cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.95,0:37:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\ren}Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.12,0:37:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\ren}Uh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.49,0:37:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定你经常听人这么说\N{\ren}I'm sure you hear this all the time but,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.09,0:37:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的眼睛是我见过的最美丽的一双\N{\ren}you have the most beautiful eyes I have ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.33,0:38:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是  我经常听人这么说\N{\ren}Yeah, I do get that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.95,0:38:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你想兑现什么面额的钞票?\N{\ren}How would you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.30,0:38:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  先生\N{\ren}Oh, I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.40,0:38:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要等银行一小时后开门才有现金\N{\ren}We won't have any cash until the banks open in an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.86,0:38:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但我肯定\N{\ren}but, uh, I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.63,0:38:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可以在飞机场给你兑现支票\N{\ren}they can cash your check at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.91,0:38:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,飞机场?\N{\ren}The airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.20,0:38:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谁在飞机场兑现支票?\N{\ren}Who cashes checks at the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.90,0:38:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,航空公司\N{\ren}Well, the airlines, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.99,0:38:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们总是给自己兑现\N{\ren}They've always taken care of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.12,0:38:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好  - 请问是要搭机吗?\N{\ren}- Hello. - Hi. Are you deadheading?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.10,0:38:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\ren}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.33,0:38:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你要搭机去迈阿密吗?\N{\ren}Are you my deadhead to Miami?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.00,0:38:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\ren}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.20,0:38:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是  我要搭机  给你\N{\ren}Yeah, I'm the deadhead. Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.20,0:39:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你有点晚了  但驾驶舱备用椅空着\N{\ren}You're a little late, but the jump seat is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.49,0:39:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我干这一行已经有段时间了\N{\ren}You know it's been awhile since I've done this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.67,0:39:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但备用椅在哪?\N{\ren}Which one's the jump seat again?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.52,0:39:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,旅途愉快\N{\ren}Have a nice flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.50,0:39:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你要搭我的飞机吗?\N{\ren}Are you my deadhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.52,0:39:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  奥利弗机长\N{\ren}Frank, Captain Oliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.47,0:39:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 约翰·拉金  副驾驶  - 你好\N{\ren}-John Larkin, the copilot. -Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.16,0:39:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,福瑞德·塔利  飞机工程师\N{\ren}Fred Tulley, flight engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.92,0:39:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克.泰勒  泛美公司\N{\ren}Frank Taylor, Pan Am.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.92,0:39:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢捎我一程  小伙子们\N{\ren}Thanks for giving me a lift, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.43,0:39:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下吧  弗兰克  我们要起飞了\N{\ren}Go ahead and take a seat, Frank. We're about to push.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.44,0:39:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你开什么飞机  DC-8?\N{\ren}What kind of equipment you on, DC-8?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.76,0:39:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是707\N{\ren}Uh, 707.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.50,0:39:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚到就返回去?\N{\ren}You turning around on the redeye?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.29,0:39:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我下几个月要在洲际之间来回飞\N{\ren}Uh, I'm jumping puddles for the next few months
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.17,0:39:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,通过给那些又病又累的人替班  来多挣点钱\N{\ren}trying to earn my keep running leapfrogs for the weak and weary.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.53,0:39:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么不好意思  我们都是这么过来的\N{\ren}No shame in that. We all did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.22,0:39:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 坐吧  - 谢谢\N{\ren}- Have a seat. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.40,0:39:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,起飞后你想喝点什么吗?\N{\ren}Would you like a drink after takeoff?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.70,0:39:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,牛奶?\N{\ren}M-Milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.35,0:39:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 速度: 80节 (时速150公里)  - 确认\N{\ren}- 80 knots. - Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.70,0:40:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 到达仰转速度  - 仰转\N{\ren}- V-one. - Rotate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.20,0:40:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 到达爬升速度  - 正仰角\N{\ren}- V-two. - Positive rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.20,0:40:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,收起落架\N{\ren}Gear up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.40,0:40:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的爸爸:\N{\ren}Dear Dad:
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.66,0:40:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我毕业\N{\ren}Today was graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.75,0:40:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在是副驾驶\N{\ren}I am now a copilot
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.87,0:40:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,每月挣1400美元  外加福利\N{\ren}earning $1,400 a month plus benefits
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.21,0:40:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而最好的一点是\N{\ren}and the best part is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.29,0:40:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他们告诉我说我的家里人可以免费飞\N{\ren}they tell me my family can fly for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.57,0:40:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以告诉妈妈去准备行李  买套新的泳衣\N{\ren}So tell Mom to pack her bags and buy a new swimsuit
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.96,0:40:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我要带你们去夏威夷过圣诞节\N{\ren}because I'm taking us all to Hawaii for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.25,0:40:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你  爸爸\N{\ren}I love you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.65,0:40:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,再见  弗兰克\N{\ren}Aloha, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.62,0:40:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好  免费乘客  - 你好\N{\ren}- Hello, deadhead. - Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.91,0:40:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,旅途愉快吗?\N{\ren}Enjoying your free ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.89,0:40:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,玛茜...\N{\ren}Marci...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.33,0:40:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是你掉的吗\N{\ren}did you drop this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.28,0:40:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一定是从你脖子上滑落下来的  - 不是\N{\ren}- Must've slipped right off your neck. - No...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.93,0:40:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我的!\N{\ren}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.01,0:40:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不...\N{\ren}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.45,0:41:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么停下来?\N{\ren}Why are you stopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.20,0:41:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我想告诉你件事  玛茜\N{\ren}I want to tell you something, Marci.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.46,0:41:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是到目前...\N{\ren}This is by far...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.73,0:41:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经有过的最好的约会\N{\ren}the best date I have ever been on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.31,0:41:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,请帮我开一个货币市场账户\N{\ren}I'd like to open a Money Market, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.49,0:41:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.75,0:41:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来迈阿密互助银行  能为您做点什么?\N{\ren}Welcome to Miami Mutual Bank. How may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.78,0:41:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫弗兰克·泰勒  是泛美航空公司的副驾驶\N{\ren}My name is Frank Taylor. I'm a copilot for Pan Am.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.70,0:42:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我想办理支票兑现\N{\ren}I'd like to cash this check here, and then
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.64,0:42:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,然后带你去吃牛排晚餐\N{\ren}I'd like to take you out for a steak dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.53,0:42:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们把支票放进磁性墨迹识别机里\N{\ren}And then we feed the checks into the MICR machine
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.64,0:42:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,它用一种特殊的墨水\N{\ren}which uses special ink
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.96,0:42:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,在支票的底部给支票加编码\N{\ren}to encode the account numbers on the bottom of the checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.20,0:42:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那些编码在哪里?\N{\ren}And where are these numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.98,0:42:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这儿\N{\ren}They're, um... right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.10,0:42:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 在这儿?  - 看到了吗?\N{\ren}- Right there? - see?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.00,0:42:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,它们叫做路由编码\N{\ren}They're called routing numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.37,0:42:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这些支票要路由到哪里去呢?\N{\ren}so where do the checks get routed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.67,0:42:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  从来没有人问过我\N{\ren}You know, I don't exactly know. Nobody ever asked me that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.54,0:42:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们下一个竞标的物品还是\N{\ren}Our next item up for bid is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.97,0:42:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来自新泽西中心银行的抵押没收品\N{\ren}from the Jersey Central Bank foreclosure.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.60,0:42:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是台磁性墨迹识别机  用来给银行支票编码的\N{\ren}This is a MICR encoder a machine used to encode bank checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.08,0:42:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有起标价吗?\N{\ren}Do I have an opening bid?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.52,0:42:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的罪犯是个从东海岸开始的伪造支票者\N{\ren}Our unknown subject is a paperhanger who started working on the East Coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.92,0:42:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在过去的几个星期里  他发明了一种\N{\ren}In the last few weeks, this unsub has developed
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.12,0:43:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,新型的支票欺诈手法  我称它"飘"\N{\ren}a new form of check fraud which I'm calling "the float."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.75,0:43:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他的做法就是\N{\ren}What he's doing is
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.84,0:43:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在不同的银行开支票帐户...\N{\ren}he's opening checking accounts at various banks
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.96,0:43:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,然后涂改那些在支票\N{\ren}then changing the MICR ink routing numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.83,0:43:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,底部的编码\N{\ren}at the bottom of those checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.22,0:43:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,请播放下一张\N{\ren}Next slide, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.72,0:43:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,下一张\N{\ren}Next slide, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.55,0:43:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,遥控器坏了\N{\ren}Uh, the remote thing is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.10,0:43:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}华盛顿特区  FBI总部
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.71,0:43:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你得手动\N{\ren}You'll have to do it by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.43,0:43:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须...  试...\N{\ren}You've gotta... try the...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.60,0:43:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,马伦探员  它因该...\N{\ren}Agent Mullen, it should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.72,0:43:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是侧面的那个方按钮\N{\ren}it should be the square button just there by the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.16,0:43:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,转盘不好使\N{\ren}This carousel doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.39,0:43:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是个坏转盘\N{\ren}It's a bad carousel you got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.64,0:43:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢  马伦探员  - 只能用手动\N{\ren}- Thank you, Agent Mullen. - Got to move it manually.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.32,0:43:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这是美联储的12个银行分布图\N{\ren}This is a map of the 12 banks of the U.s. Federal Reserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.18,0:43:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,下一张\N{\ren}slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.30,0:43:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,每个银行的识别机的扫描仪\N{\ren}MICR scanners at every bank
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.09,0:43:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,读取支票底部的这些数字  下一张\N{\ren}read these numbers at the bottom of a check... slide...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.00,0:43:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,然后把支票发送到相关的银行兑现\N{\ren}and then, ship that check off to its corresponding branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.50,0:43:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔  对我们这些不熟悉银行诈骗的\N{\ren}Carl, for those of us who are unfamiliar with bank fraud
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.42,0:43:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能告诉我们  你在讲什么?\N{\ren}you mind telling us what the hell you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.50,0:43:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,东海岸分行的编号是从01到06\N{\ren}The East Coast branches are numbered zero-one to zero-six.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.56,0:43:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,中部地区分行的编号是07到08\N{\ren}The central branch is zero-seven, zero-eight
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.63,0:43:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如此类推\N{\ren}so on, so forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.33,0:43:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,底部的那些号码\N{\ren}You mean those numbers on the bottom of a check
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.83,0:43:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么实际意思吗?\N{\ren}actually mean something?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.93,0:43:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这些都是我两天前做的报告\N{\ren}All of this was in the report I filed two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.15,0:44:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你把02改成12  这就意味着...\N{\ren}If you change... a zero-two to a one-two
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.30,0:44:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这就意味着在纽约提现金的支票\N{\ren}that means that check, which was cashed in New York
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.84,0:44:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不会再转到纽约联邦分行了\N{\ren}is not go to the New York Federal Branch
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.49,0:44:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而是会被转到... 都回到旧金山分行\N{\ren}but it is rerouted all the way to the san Francisco Federal Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.90,0:44:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,银行在两个星期里  不会知道支票已被退回了\N{\ren}The bank doesn't even know the check has bounced for two weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.40,0:44:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这就意味着我们的犯人会待在一个地方\N{\ren}which means our unsub can stay in one place
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.16,0:44:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在同一个城市不断重施故技\N{\ren}paper the same city over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.85,0:44:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,直至支票送经全国\N{\ren}while his checks circle the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.45,0:44:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该和我的太太谈谈\N{\ren}You know, you want to talk to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.88,0:44:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们家她管支票本\N{\ren}she's the one balances the checkbook at our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.37,0:44:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,下一张\N{\ren}Next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.49,0:44:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸!\N{\ren}Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.22,0:44:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子  飞行员\N{\ren}My son, the birdman.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.25,0:44:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,穿制服了\N{\ren}some uniform, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.30,0:44:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样?\N{\ren}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.34,0:44:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\ren}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.03,0:44:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,坐吧\N{\ren}sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.77,0:44:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  你收到明信片了吗?\N{\ren}so, Dad... Daddy, have you gotten the postcards?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.97,0:44:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\ren}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.33,0:44:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这叉子冰凉\N{\ren}This fork is ice cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.65,0:45:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不  爸爸  那是冰镇的吃沙拉用的叉子\N{\ren}No, no, Dad, th-that's a chilled salad fork.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.37,0:45:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个高档餐厅  你知道\N{\ren}It's a fancy restaurant, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.54,0:45:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿\N{\ren}Well, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.99,0:45:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我有东西送你  - 什么东西?\N{\ren}- I-I got you something. - What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.00,0:45:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,打开看看\N{\ren}Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.40,0:45:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那些是什么  对吧?\N{\ren}You know what those are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.18,0:45:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一辆1965年卡迪拉克敞篷车的钥匙\N{\ren}Those are the keys to a 1965 Cadillac DeVille convertible.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.20,0:45:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,全新的  爸爸\N{\ren}Brand-new, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.68,0:45:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,车身红色  车内白色...\N{\ren}Red with white interior
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.63,0:45:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,分开的座位  空调  全套的配置\N{\ren}split seats, air conditioning, the works.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.83,0:45:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你送给我一辆卡迪拉克?\N{\ren}Are you giving me a Cadillac?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.44,0:45:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我送给你一辆卡迪拉克\N{\ren}Yeah. I'm giving you a Cadillac.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.16,0:45:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  它就停在楼下\N{\ren}Dad, sh-she's parked downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.55,0:45:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们吃完午饭后\N{\ren}When we're done eating lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.59,0:45:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就开到妈妈那里去...\N{\ren}why don't you, you know, drive on over to Mom's house
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.21,0:45:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,带上她兜兜风\N{\ren}pick her up, take a little joyride?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.37,0:45:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果税务局发现我开辆新的双门轿车到处跑\N{\ren}Do you know what would happen if the IRs found out
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.54,0:45:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道会发生什么?\N{\ren}I was driving around in a new coupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.10,0:45:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我坐火车来的  弗兰克\N{\ren}I took the train here, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.46,0:46:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,也要坐火车回去\N{\ren}I'm taking the train home.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.31,0:46:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\ren}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.35,0:46:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我有很多钱\N{\ren}I have plenty of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.81,0:46:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  需要什么尽管讲\N{\ren}You know, if you ever, ever need anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.26,0:46:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你担心我?\N{\ren}You worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.82,0:46:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,担心我?\N{\ren}About me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.90,0:46:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不是担心\N{\ren}No, I'm not... I'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.84,0:46:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我自己买不起车?\N{\ren}You think I can't buy my own car?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.08,0:46:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,两只老鼠掉进奶油桶里  弗兰克\N{\ren}Two mice fell in a bucket of cream, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.95,0:46:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我是哪只?\N{\ren}Which one am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.86,0:46:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你是第二只老鼠\N{\ren}You're that second mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.43,0:46:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天路过商店\N{\ren}I went by the store today.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.57,0:46:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不把商店关几天\N{\ren}I had to close the store for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.42,0:46:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只是个时间问题  弗兰克\N{\ren}It's all about timing, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.99,0:46:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,狗屁政府清楚这点\N{\ren}The goddamn government knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.77,0:46:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他们落井下石\N{\ren}They hit you when you're down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.37,0:46:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让他们把商店夺走  所以我就...\N{\ren}I wasn't going to let them take it from me, so I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.38,0:46:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,干脆自己关了店门  看他们能把我怎样\N{\ren}shut the doors myself, called their bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.60,0:46:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,早晚他们是要忘了我的\N{\ren}sooner or later, they'll forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.31,0:46:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\ren}I understand, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.12,0:47:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉妈了吗?\N{\ren}Have you told Ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.42,0:47:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你母亲  她很固执\N{\ren}she's so stubborn, your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.49,0:47:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要担心  我不会不劝她就让她走的\N{\ren}Don't worry. I'm not going to let her go without a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.53,0:47:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我要劝她为我们留下...\N{\ren}I been fighting for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.33,0:47:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸?\N{\ren}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.00,0:47:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,从我们相遇的那天起\N{\ren}since the day we... we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.99,0:47:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  在那些人当中...\N{\ren}Daddy, out of all those men
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.91,0:47:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是你赢得了妈妈的心  记得吗?\N{\ren}you were the one that took her home, remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.72,0:47:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,200人坐在那个小厅里看她跳舞\N{\ren}200 men, sitting in that tiny social hall watching her dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.24,0:47:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那个小镇叫什么名字来着?\N{\ren}What was the name of that town?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.98,0:47:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 曼沙  爸爸  - 是的\N{\ren}- Montrichard, Dad. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.42,0:47:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我一句法语也不会说\N{\ren}I didn't speak a word of French
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.52,0:47:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而六个星期后  她成了我的妻子\N{\ren}and six weeks later, she was my wi...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.19,0:47:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她还是你的妻子\N{\ren}she's your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.19,0:47:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我儿子今天给我买了辆卡迪拉克\N{\ren}My son bought me a Cadillac today.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.97,0:48:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想该为此干一杯\N{\ren}I think that calls for a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.15,0:48:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,为了天空中最好的飞行员\N{\ren}To the best damn pilot in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.54,0:48:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不像你想的那样\N{\ren}It's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.27,0:48:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是名副驾驶\N{\ren}I'm just a copilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.82,0:48:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见这些人在注视你吗?\N{\ren}You see these people staring at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.87,0:48:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是纽约市最有权势的人\N{\ren}These are the most powerful people in New York City
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.38,0:48:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们总是越过肩膀偷看\N{\ren}and they keep peeking over their shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.67,0:48:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,想知道今晚你去哪里\N{\ren}wondering where you're going tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.30,0:48:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里  弗兰克?\N{\ren}Where you going, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.99,0:48:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  没有人在盯着我\N{\ren}Dad, nobody's staring at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.94,0:48:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什么奇异的地方吗?\N{\ren}some place exotic?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.00,0:48:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你要去哪里\N{\ren}Just tell me where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.74,0:48:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,洛杉... 好莱坞\N{\ren}Los An... Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.11,0:48:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好莱坞?\N{\ren}Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.68,0:48:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们其余的人...\N{\ren}The rest of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.88,0:49:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真是笨蛋\N{\ren}really are suckers.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.04,0:49:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我穿了这红衣服和高跟鞋  对吗?\N{\ren}so, I got on this red dress and these high heels, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.32,0:49:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我外边这儿戴了胸罩\N{\ren}And I got a bra, like, out here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.15,0:49:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我追两个波多黎各人\N{\ren}And I'm chasing these two Puerto Rican guys
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.60,0:49:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}加利福尼亚  好莱坞
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.26,0:49:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,在公园里\N{\ren}through the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.62,0:49:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他们拎一个装满了从银行抢来的钱的箱子\N{\ren}They got a suitcase filled with bank robbery loot.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.30,0:49:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我大喊: "联邦调查局  不许动! "\N{\ren}Okay, I'm screaming out, "FBI, freeze!"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.84,0:49:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拿枪  却发现不在胸罩里\N{\ren}And I'm reaching for my gun, but I can't find it in the bra.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.25,0:49:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它太他妈大了\N{\ren}It's so damn big
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.46,0:49:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我会不会把乳头射掉\N{\ren}I thought I was going to shoot my tits off.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.40,0:49:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个有趣的故事\N{\ren}You know, that's a funny story.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.68,0:49:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,别人总是被逗笑\N{\ren}People always laugh at that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.65,0:49:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,让我问你一个问题  阿穆德斯基先生\N{\ren}Let me ask you a question, Mr. Amdursky.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.69,0:49:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你觉得当便衣很有意思\N{\ren}If you were having so much fun undercover
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.72,0:49:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么转到银行诈骗科?\N{\ren}why did you transfer to bank fraud?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.53,0:49:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我要求转的\N{\ren}I didn't transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.55,0:49:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我受责难被重分配的\N{\ren}I was censured and reassigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.42,0:49:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是受罚了 我就受罚了\N{\ren}It's like being punished. I was punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.11,0:49:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我出外勤时犯了个错误\N{\ren}I screwed up in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.90,0:49:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢?  福克斯先生\N{\ren}What about you, Mr. Fox?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.38,0:49:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有在出外勤时  因为犯错而受罚过?\N{\ren}Were you... punished for screwing up in the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.32,0:49:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  我以前从没穿便衣去调查过\N{\ren}Oh, no, no, no, I've never worked in the field before.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.55,0:49:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我在司法部的文职申请部审计背景调查\N{\ren}I audited background investigations of Department of Justice clerical applicants.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.96,0:49:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了  我要一队便衣\N{\ren}Well, that's just great. I ask for a team
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.46,0:49:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,结果他们给我派了两个不称职的人\N{\ren}and they drag the bottom of the Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.79,0:50:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我能问你个问题吗?  汉拉蒂探员\N{\ren}You mind if I ask you a question, Agent Handratty?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.44,0:50:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么总是那么严肃?\N{\ren}How come you're so serious all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.88,0:50:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这干扰你了吗  阿穆德斯基先生?\N{\ren}Does it bother you, Mr. Amdursky?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.10,0:50:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对  是干扰我了\N{\ren}Yeah. Yeah, it does bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.88,0:50:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,干扰你了吗  福克斯先生?\N{\ren}Does it bother you, Mr. Fox?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.90,0:50:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我想有一点\N{\ren}A little, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.50,0:50:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你们想听我讲个笑话吗?\N{\ren}Well, would you like to hear me tell a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.64,0:50:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,想  我们很想听你讲个笑话\N{\ren}Yeah. Yeah, we'd love to hear a joke from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.56,0:50:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,咚咚敲门\N{\ren}Knock, knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.83,0:50:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁?\N{\ren}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.10,0:50:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,去你妈的\N{\ren}Go fuck yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.87,0:50:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻可爱  高挑棕肤\N{\ren}Tall and tan and young and lovely
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.33,0:50:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这来自Ipanema的女孩\N{\ren}The girl from Ipanema...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.53,0:50:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他兑换了三张支票  都取到钱了\N{\ren}He cashed three checks. They all cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.95,0:50:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天打算存这张\N{\ren}I was going to deposit this one today.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.89,0:50:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想有麻烦\N{\ren}I don't want any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.60,0:50:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没有麻烦\N{\ren}No trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.75,0:50:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也没有\N{\ren}No trouble at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.30,0:50:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就拿着这张支票上路了\N{\ren}We'll just take this check and be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.70,0:50:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢  - 很好\N{\ren}- Thank you. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.38,0:51:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不想让我的顾客受到干扰\N{\ren}Because I don't want my customers harassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.45,0:51:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么?  他仍然在这儿吗?\N{\ren}What are you saying, he's still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.30,0:51:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,201房间\N{\ren}201.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.64,0:51:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\ren}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.55,0:51:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 到转弯了  - 谢谢  儿子\N{\ren}- Corner here. - Oh, thanks, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.40,0:51:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有楼梯  - 楼梯\N{\ren}- some steps. - steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.15,0:51:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,墨菲先生  你好吗?\N{\ren}Hey, Mr. Murphy, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.19,0:51:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是弗兰克吗?  - 是我\N{\ren}- Is that Frank? - Yeah, it's Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.68,0:51:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 弗兰克  你好吗?  - 您膝盖怎么样了?\N{\ren}- Hey, Frank, how are you? - How's the knee?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.87,0:51:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,得了  我现在就跟你赛跑\N{\ren}Come on, I'll race you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.15,0:51:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 小心点  - 好的\N{\ren}- Take care. - Okay, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.04,0:51:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,得了  卡尔  这个家伙是个文人\N{\ren}Come on, Carl, this guy's a pen and ink man.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.60,0:51:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这个该死的裱糊工  他连枪都没带\N{\ren}A goddamn paperhanger. He doesn't even carry a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.33,0:51:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为什么不和你一起走  卡尔?  \N{\ren}Why can't we go with you, Carl?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.65,0:51:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,打起精神好好干  我会给你俩买冰激凌吃\N{\ren}You just keep your eyes open, do your job and I'll buy you both a Good Humor bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.80,0:51:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  夫人  联邦调查局\N{\ren}It's all right, ma'am. FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.51,0:52:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,201室\N{\ren}201... 201, 201.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.60,0:52:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局!\N{\ren}FBI!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.40,0:52:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局!\N{\ren}FBI!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.10,0:52:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,从卫生间出来!\N{\ren}Come out of the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.46,0:52:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,从卫生间出来!\N{\ren}step out of the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.59,0:52:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,手放在头上\N{\ren}Hands on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.73,0:52:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是新的IBM电动打字机\N{\ren}Oh, that's the new IBM selectric.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.63,0:52:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,把手放到头上\N{\ren}Put your hands on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.53,0:52:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,五秒钟内就能改变打印格式\N{\ren}You can change the print type in five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.69,0:52:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 闭嘴!  - 只是突出了个球.\N{\ren}-Shut up! -Just pop out the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.13,0:52:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,把手放到头上!\N{\ren}Put your hands on your head! Put your hands...!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.19,0:52:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他有200多张支票  1加仑印度墨水\N{\ren}You know, he's got over 200 checks here, a gallon
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.75,0:52:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还有草图  - 举起手\N{\ren}- of India ink, drafting. - Hands on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.35,0:52:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至发自泛美的薪水信封都写着\N{\ren}Even has little payroll envelopes addressed to himself
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.35,0:52:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他自己的地址  - 放下!  扔掉!\N{\ren}- from Pan Am. - Put it down! Drop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.85,0:52:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,放松点!\N{\ren}Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.40,0:52:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你来晚了  我是巴里·艾伦\N{\ren}You're late, all right? My name's Allen, Barry Allen
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.75,0:52:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,美国特情局的\N{\ren}United states secret service.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.92,0:52:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你的嫌疑犯刚才想从窗户跳出去\N{\ren}Your boy just tried to jump out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.87,0:52:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,被我同伴拘捕了  \N{\ren}My partner has him in custody downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.18,0:53:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你少鬼扯\N{\ren}I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.20,0:53:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为只有联邦调查局在追捕他吗?\N{\ren}You think the FBI are the only ones on this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.89,0:53:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是说\N{\ren}I mean, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.46,0:53:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,别争了  他在这里还在伪造政府支票\N{\ren}Come on, he's dabbling in government checks here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.21,0:53:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是根据这张才跟踪到他的\N{\ren}We've been following a paper trail on this guy
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.37,0:53:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,已经有好几个月了\N{\ren}for months now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.49,0:53:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你介意把枪从我的脸上移开吗?\N{\ren}Hey, you mind taking that gun out of my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.33,0:53:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了  真的  这让我感觉紧张\N{\ren}Please. Really. I mean, it makes me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.61,0:53:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 让我看看你的证件  - 当然\N{\ren}- Let me see some credentials. - Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.00,0:53:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,把我的钱包都拿去吧\N{\ren}Take my whole wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.12,0:53:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你还想要我的枪?  你来拿好了\N{\ren}You want my gun, too? Come over here. Take my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.96,0:53:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,帮个忙  看窗外  看\N{\ren}Hey, hey, look, just do me a favor. Take a look outside. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.09,0:53:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看看窗外\N{\ren}Look out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.14,0:53:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我的同伴正押着他走向那车  看\N{\ren}My partner's walking him to the car as we speak... Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.55,0:53:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,在我进来时  老家伙差点尿裤子\N{\ren}Old guy almost pissed in his pants when I came through the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.41,0:53:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他直接从这窗户跳到我的车上\N{\ren}He jumped right through the window onto the hood of my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.54,0:53:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 墨菲?  - 嗯?\N{\ren}- Hey, Murph? -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.80,0:53:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,给洛杉矶警察局打电话\N{\ren}Call the LAPD again.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.09,0:53:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让人走进我的犯罪现场\N{\ren}I don't want people walking through my crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.95,0:53:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想到情报局卷了进来\N{\ren}I didn't expect the secret service on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.70,0:53:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心\N{\ren}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.35,0:53:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字?\N{\ren}Well, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.22,0:54:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,汉莱提  卡尔·汉莱提\N{\ren}Handratty, Carl Handratty.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.20,0:54:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看一下你的证件吗?\N{\ren}Mind if I see some identification?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.79,0:54:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当然  - 小心驶得万年船\N{\ren}- sure. - You never can be too careful these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.27,0:54:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,运气不好  卡尔\N{\ren}Well, tough luck, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.45,0:54:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,早来5分钟  你就能抓个正着\N{\ren}Five minutes earlier you would've landed yourself a pretty good collar.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.35,0:54:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\ren}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.36,0:54:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要是晚来10秒钟  就被打死了\N{\ren}Ten seconds later, and you'd have been shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.45,0:54:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,介意我跟你一起去吗?\N{\ren}Mind if I come downstairs with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.98,0:54:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我得看看这家伙  - 当然行\N{\ren}- I got to take a look at this guy. - Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.28,0:54:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,帮个忙  在这等我下\N{\ren}Just, uh, do me a favor and sit tight for a second
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.46,0:54:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我下楼去取证据\N{\ren}while I get this evidence downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.14,0:54:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让服务员进来铺床\N{\ren}You know, I don't want some maid walking through here and making the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.98,0:54:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 洛杉矶警察局的人随时会到  - 等等\N{\ren}- LAPD should be here any sec. - Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.00,0:54:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你的钱包\N{\ren}Your wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.30,0:54:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,替我保管一会儿  我相信你\N{\ren}You hang onto it for a minute. I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.19,0:55:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,情报局\N{\ren}secret service.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.69,0:55:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼!\N{\ren}Oh, goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.84,0:55:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真愚蠢\N{\ren}It was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.46,0:55:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我犯了个愚蠢的错误\N{\ren}I made a stupid mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.38,0:55:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别想了\N{\ren}Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.02,0:56:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,还有百多宗没破的案件\N{\ren}There are hundreds of unknown subjects out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.55,0:56:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我能抓住这家伙\N{\ren}I-I can get this guy, sean.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.16,0:56:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,造假的人所做的最糟糕的事  就是被人看见脸\N{\ren}The worst thing a paperhanger can do is show his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.84,0:56:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了报告\N{\ren}I read the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.60,0:56:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,1米80高  棕色头发  27到30岁之间\N{\ren}six feet tall, brown hair, 27 to 30 years of age
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.02,0:56:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,70公斤\N{\ren}160 pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.20,0:56:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的人到处都是\N{\ren}This could be almost anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.55,0:56:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我听见了他的声音  看到了他的脸\N{\ren}I heard his voice, Sean, I saw his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.88,0:56:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有什么可掩藏的了\N{\ren}There's nothing for him to hide behind anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.22,0:56:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,小心些\N{\ren}Just be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.00,0:56:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你干了12年了\N{\ren}You got 12 years in.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.85,0:56:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人干扰你的工作\N{\ren}Nobody bothers you down on the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.72,0:56:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你写了那本银行诈骗案的书\N{\ren}You practically wrote the book on bank fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.75,0:56:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那会让你有一天成为部门主管的\N{\ren}That's the kind of thing that can make you section chief someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.80,0:56:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要把自己放到那种位置上\N{\ren}Just don't put yourself in this type of position.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.05,0:56:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哪种位置?\N{\ren}What type of position?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.30,0:56:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,受辱的位置\N{\ren}Position of being humiliated.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.00,0:56:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你想听我讲个笑话吗?\N{\ren}sean, would you like to hear me tell a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.06,0:56:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧\N{\ren}Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.28,0:56:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,咚咚敲门\N{\ren}Knock, knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.02,0:57:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我的下个问题是  飞行员退休后...\N{\ren}so, my-my next question is, when a pilot retires
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.66,0:57:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,泛美每个月都给他们发张支票吗?\N{\ren}uh, Pan Am sends them a check every single month?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.72,0:57:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对  按养老金计划给他们发支票和福利\N{\ren}Uh, yeah, pension program sends a check and benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.68,0:57:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,支票上有多少钱?\N{\ren}How much is that check for?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.08,0:57:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在没有心情谈这个\N{\ren}Uh, kid, I'm really not in the mood for this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.17,0:57:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那个空中强盗都快把我搞疯了\N{\ren}This skywayman's driving me crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.42,0:57:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个强盗?\N{\ren}Who's the skywayman?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.66,0:57:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一个假扮成泛美飞行员  到处飞的疯子\N{\ren}Ah, some nut that's flying around the country posing as a Pan Am pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.89,0:57:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,今天报纸有他的一个栏目\N{\ren}There's a column about him in the paper today.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.01,0:57:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不断告诉他们说这不是我的问题\N{\ren}I keep telling them this is not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.91,0:57:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙甚至不飞泛美\N{\ren}This guy doesn't even fly Pan Am.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.02,0:57:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他飞别的公司\N{\ren}Flies everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.07,0:57:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他飞联合  环球  大陆  东部...\N{\ren}Flies United, TWA, Continental, Eastern...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.05,0:57:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,空中强盗\N{\ren}The skywayman.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.26,0:57:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,报界喜欢这小丑\N{\ren}Newspaper loves this clown.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.40,0:57:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他们称他为空中的詹姆斯·邦德\N{\ren}They call him "the James Bond of the sky."
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.40,0:57:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你说...?  - 邦德  詹姆斯.邦德\N{\ren}- Did you say...? - Bond, James Bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.97,0:58:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我  琼  他为什么那样做?\N{\ren}Tell me, Joan, why does he do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.80,0:58:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他喜欢赢  - 快点  快点\N{\ren}- He likes to win. - Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.46,0:58:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们20分钟就会着陆.\N{\ren}We'll be landing in 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.31,0:58:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你想玩简单的还是玩难的?\N{\ren}Do you want to play it easy or the hard way?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.55,0:58:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是镇静剂.\N{\ren}And this isn't a tranquilizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.24,0:58:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  普茜  你对飞机的了解要比枪多得多\N{\ren}Well, Pussy, you do know a lot more about planes than guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.19,0:58:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  普茜\N{\ren}Hello, Pussy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.30,0:58:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你肯定是这种西装?  - 肯定\N{\ren}- Now, you're sure this is the suit, right? - Positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.63,0:58:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他在电影里穿的完全一样\N{\ren}It's the exact suit he wore in the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.49,0:58:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我买3套\N{\ren}Okay. I'll take three.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.16,0:58:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题  弗莱明先生\N{\ren}Certainly, Mr. Fleming.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.91,0:58:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你缺的就是一辆\N{\ren}Now what you need is one of those
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.58,0:58:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他开的那种外国小跑车\N{\ren}little foreign sports cars that he drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.55,0:58:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\ren}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.30,0:59:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前见过你吗?\N{\ren}Haven't I seen you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.55,0:59:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,也许\N{\ren}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.60,0:59:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,几年以前我上过《17岁》 的封面\N{\ren}A couple years ago, I was on the cover of Seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.98,0:59:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是那个模特  对吗?  谢丽尔\N{\ren}You're that model, right? Cheryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.34,0:59:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是\N{\ren}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.36,0:59:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我同学总喜欢把你的照片贴在存衣柜里\N{\ren}The guys used to put your picture on their lockers.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.08,0:59:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见的停在外面的那辆银色轿车  是你的吗?\N{\ren}Isn't that your silver car I saw parked out front?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.25,0:59:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对  其中一辆\N{\ren}Yeah. One of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.74,0:59:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  能给我签个名吗?\N{\ren}so, think I could get an autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.69,0:59:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你房间里有笔吗?\N{\ren}Do you have a pen in your room?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.43,1:00:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,像你这样的人可以买任何想要的东西\N{\ren}Man like you can buy anything he wants.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.10,1:00:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他在旅馆的礼品店里买了一副纸牌\N{\ren}He buys a deck of cards at the hotel gift shop.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.33,1:00:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你想看我耍扑克把戏吗?\N{\ren}Well, you want to see a card trick?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.00,1:00:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这扑克价值多少钱?\N{\ren}How much did these cards cost?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.59,1:00:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想55分吧\N{\ren}Oh, 55 cents, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.53,1:00:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果楼下旅馆的礼品店里把我卖了\N{\ren}And if they sold me downstairs at the hotel gift shop...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.55,1:01:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你会付多少钱?\N{\ren}how much would you pay?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.40,1:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对...\N{\ren}I'm sor...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.53,1:01:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  我给什么付多少钱?\N{\ren}I'm sorry, how mu... how much would I pay for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.66,1:01:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,一整夜\N{\ren}The entire night.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.21,1:01:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我陪你一整晚你付我多少钱?\N{\ren}How much would you pay me for the entire night?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.27,1:01:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢丽尔  我真不知道\N{\ren}Cheryl, I... I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.83,1:01:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要害怕\N{\ren}Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.75,1:01:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,出个价\N{\ren}Make me an offer.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.61,1:01:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,300美元?\N{\ren}$300?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.51,1:01:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,抓牌\N{\ren}Go fish.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.90,1:01:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,500美元?\N{\ren}Uh, 500 dollars?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.20,1:01:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,抓牌\N{\ren}Go fish.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.97,1:01:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,600美元?\N{\ren}$600.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.90,1:02:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,抓牌!\N{\ren}Go fish.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.55,1:02:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,1000美元\N{\ren}$1,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.78,1:02:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.85,1:02:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,1000美元\N{\ren}$1,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.25,1:02:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.30,1:02:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上就回来\N{\ren}I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.90,1:02:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  你去哪儿?\N{\ren}Wait a second. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.70,1:02:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我下楼去兑现支票\N{\ren}I'm going downstairs to cash a check.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.08,1:02:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你想旅馆能给你兑现1000美元支票?\N{\ren}You think this hotel is going to cash a $1,000 check
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.94,1:02:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,凌晨3点?\N{\ren}at 3:00am?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.80,1:02:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是张纽约储蓄和贷款支票\N{\ren}It's a New York savings and Loan check.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.87,1:02:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,像金子一样  他们会给兑现的\N{\ren}It's like gold. They'll cash it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.13,1:02:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得他们可能会产生点怀疑吗?\N{\ren}Don't you think they might get a little suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.14,1:02:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看\N{\ren}Let me see that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.83,1:02:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是银行开出的支票  背书给我\N{\ren}It's a cashier's check. Endorse it over to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.68,1:02:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能那么做\N{\ren}No. I couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.52,1:02:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这张支票是1400美元的\N{\ren}see, this check is for $1,400.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.32,1:02:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们谈好的价是1000美元\N{\ren}We agreed upon $1,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.02,1:02:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我不能给你400美元  \N{\ren}Why don't I give you back $400
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.93,1:02:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你给我那支票呢?\N{\ren}and you give me that check?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.20,1:02:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那更好\N{\ren}Even better.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.52,1:03:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是谁的吗?\N{\ren}Does this belong to anybody?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.35,1:03:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是汉莱提  圣诞快乐\N{\ren}This is Handratty. Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.38,1:03:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  卡尔\N{\ren}Hello, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.40,1:03:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\ren}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.00,1:04:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,巴里·艾伦  情报局的\N{\ren}Barry Allen, secret service.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.20,1:04:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,过去几个小时里  我一直在找你\N{\ren}I've been trying to track you down now for the last couple of hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.20,1:04:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要怎样?\N{\ren}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.01,1:04:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我想为在洛杉矶发生的事向你道歉\N{\ren}I wanted to apologize for what happened in Los Angeles.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.98,1:04:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不要向我道歉\N{\ren}No, no, you don't apologize to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.69,1:04:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你平安夜也总是在工作吗?\N{\ren}Do you always work on Christmas Eve, Carl?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.56,1:04:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我自愿...\N{\ren}I volunteered
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.80,1:04:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以有家的人可以早点回家了\N{\ren}so men with families could go home early.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.71,1:04:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好像你戴着个结婚戒指来的\N{\ren}Looked like you were wearing a wedding ring
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.42,1:04:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你有家呢\N{\ren}I thought maybe you had a family.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.95,1:04:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我没有家\N{\ren}No. No family.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.41,1:04:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你想跟我谈谈吗?\N{\ren}You want to talk to me...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.49,1:04:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们见面谈吧  - 行\N{\ren}- let's talk face-to-face. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.42,1:04:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我在斯戴弗桑阿姆斯的办公室  3113房间\N{\ren}I'm at my suite at the stuyvesant Arms, room 3113.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.52,1:04:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,早上我要出发  去拉斯维加斯度周末\N{\ren}In the morning, I leave for Las Vegas for the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.07,1:04:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你想再耍我一次吗?\N{\ren}You think you're going to get me again?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.85,1:04:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你去不了拉斯维加斯\N{\ren}You're not going to Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.67,1:04:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不在斯戴弗桑阿姆斯\N{\ren}You're not in the stuyvesant Arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.85,1:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我在平安夜派20名特工  \N{\ren}You'd love for me to send out 20 agents Christmas Eve
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.94,1:04:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,冲进你的旅馆  撞开你的门\N{\ren}we barge into your hotel, knock down the door
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.68,1:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你可以耍我们大家\N{\ren}so you can make fools out of us all.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.10,1:05:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我耍弄了你我真的很抱歉\N{\ren}I'm really sorry if I made a fool out of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.59,1:05:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的  - 不需要\N{\ren}- I really am. - Uh-uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.66,1:05:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  听我说  我是真的\N{\ren}No, listen, I really am.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.06,1:05:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你不要对我有歉意\N{\ren}No, no, you-you do not feel sorry for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.46,1:05:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  我知道是你\N{\ren}The truth is, I knew it was you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.84,1:05:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有给你戴上手铐  但我知道\N{\ren}Now maybe I didn't get the cuffs on you, but I knew.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.05,1:05:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,人们只知道你告诉他们的  卡尔\N{\ren}Ah, people only know what you tell them, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.65,1:05:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你告诉我  情报局的巴里·艾伦\N{\ren}Well, then tell me this, Barry Allen, secret service.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.33,1:05:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我不会看你的钱包?\N{\ren}How did you know I wouldn't look in your wallet?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.30,1:05:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,与杨基队为什么总赢一样的道理\N{\ren}The same reason the Yankees always win.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.38,1:05:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人能把眼睛从条纹衣服上移开\N{\ren}Nobody can keep their eyes off the pinstripes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.59,1:05:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,杨基对能赢是因为有了米基.曼托\N{\ren}The Yankees win because they have Mickey Mantle.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.90,1:05:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,从来没有人对他们的服装下赌注\N{\ren}No one ever bets on the uniform.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.29,1:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定这点吗  卡尔?\N{\ren}You sure about that, Carl?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.72,1:05:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你我能肯定什么\N{\ren}I'll tell you what I am sure of.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.23,1:05:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定是要被抓住的\N{\ren}You're going to get caught.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.58,1:05:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这样或是那样  只是个数学问题\N{\ren}One way or another, it's a mathematical fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.60,1:05:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就像在赌城\N{\ren}It's-It's like Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.12,1:05:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,总是庄家赢\N{\ren}The House always wins.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.40,1:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔  对不起  我得结束谈话了\N{\ren}Well, Carl, I'm sorry, but I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.50,1:06:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你打电话不只是为了道歉  对吗?\N{\ren}Ah. You didn't call just to apologize, did you?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.54,1:06:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么意思?\N{\ren}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.49,1:06:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你没别人可打电话\N{\ren}You... you... you have no one else to call.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.69,1:06:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把那个汉堡拿起来  - 好的\N{\ren}- You got that burger up? - Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.34,1:06:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗?\N{\ren}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.13,1:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,再加点咖啡吗, 先生?\N{\ren}More coffee, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.86,1:06:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你是收藏家吗?\N{\ren}Are you a collector?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.65,1:06:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哪方面的?\N{\ren}Of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.57,1:07:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,《宇宙之光的俘虏》 《大冻结》\N{\ren}"Captives of the Cosmic Ray," "The Big Freeze"
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.30,1:07:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,《金色巨人之地》  我都收集全了\N{\ren}"Land of the Golden Giants." I've got them all.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.64,1:07:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么?\N{\ren}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.63,1:07:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,巴里·艾伦\N{\ren}Barry Allen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.95,1:07:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"闪电"\N{\ren}The Flash.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.17,1:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  孩子  过来\N{\ren}Wait, kid, kid, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.20,1:07:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你指  就像这本漫画书?\N{\ren}You mean like the comic book?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.01,1:07:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对  就是这漫画书  当他不是"闪电"时\N{\ren}Yeah, the comic book. When he's not The Flash.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.89,1:07:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,巴里·艾伦就是他的名字\N{\ren}That's his name, Barry Allen.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.90,1:07:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\ren}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.30,1:07:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,听清楚了  他读漫画书!\N{\ren}Now get this: He reads comic books.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.32,1:07:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,漫画书!  巴里·艾伦是"闪电" !\N{\ren}Comic books! Barry Allen is The Flash!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.16,1:07:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔  慢点儿  我不知道你在说什么\N{\ren}Carl, slow down. I don't know what the hell you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.37,1:07:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个孩子  我们的目标是个孩子\N{\ren}He's a kid. Our unsub is a kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.41,1:07:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怪不得我们对不上他的指纹\N{\ren}That's why we couldn't match his prints.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.92,1:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有犯罪记录\N{\ren}That's why he doesn't have a record.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.00,1:07:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,联系纽约警察局\N{\ren}Now, I want you to contact NYPD
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.08,1:07:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,查一下所有离家出走的年轻人的情况\N{\ren}for every all-points juvenile runaways in New York City.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.37,1:07:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,别忘了飞机场\N{\ren}And don't forget the airports.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.55,1:07:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他到处洒支票\N{\ren}He's been kiting checks all over the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.48,1:07:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么是纽约?  - 因为杨基队!\N{\ren}- But why New York? - The Yankees!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.98,1:07:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他说过杨基队的事情!\N{\ren}He said something about the Yankees!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.76,1:07:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到名单哪儿了?\N{\ren}so where are we on the list?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.77,1:08:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,53号  阿巴戈内尔\N{\ren}Number 53, "Abagnahlee."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.25,1:08:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,早晨好  女士\N{\ren}Good morning, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.16,1:08:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是打电话的联邦调查局特工\N{\ren}We're the FBI agents who called.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.00,1:08:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我在等你们  我想你们都饿了\N{\ren}Yes, I've been waiting. I hope you're all hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.43,1:08:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在解冻沙拉丽蛋糕\N{\ren}I put out the sara Lee.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.27,1:08:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我的丈夫杰克是名律师\N{\ren}My husband Jack is a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.21,1:08:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你的第一任丈夫怎样了 阿巴戈内里太太?\N{\ren}What about your first husband, Mrs. "Abagnahlee"?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.98,1:08:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,阿巴戈内尔  但我喜欢被称为巴恩斯\N{\ren}Abagnale, but I prefer to be called Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.64,1:08:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"弗兰克·威廉·阿巴戈内尔"\N{\ren}"Frank William Abagnale."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.56,1:08:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,据说他服过役\N{\ren}It says here he was in the service.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.86,1:08:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是在大战时认识的?\N{\ren}Did... Did you two meet during the war?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.75,1:08:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我住的一个很小的村庄里\N{\ren}Yeah, I lived in a very small village
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.14,1:08:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在法国...  叫曼沙\N{\ren}in France... Montrichard.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.30,1:08:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那种地方的人从来都没听说过沙拉丽\N{\ren}the kind of place where they never heard of sara Lee.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.86,1:08:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,请便\N{\ren}Help yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.91,1:08:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,没人不喜欢沙拉丽\N{\ren}"Nobody doesn't like sara Lee."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.67,1:08:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你填写过一份离家出走少年的失踪报告\N{\ren}You filled out a missing person's report for a runaway juvenile
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.03,1:08:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,名叫小弗兰克·阿巴戈内尔\N{\ren}by the name of Frank Abagnale Jr.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.27,1:08:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克没事吧?\N{\ren}Is Frankie okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.18,1:08:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他在美国大通银行的...\N{\ren}You're aware of the fact that he wrote some checks
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.69,1:08:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,死账户上开支票吗?\N{\ren}on a closed account at Chase Manhattan Bank?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.23,1:08:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,知道\N{\ren}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.40,1:08:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,警察认为他犯了某种罪\N{\ren}The police think he's some type of criminal.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.87,1:09:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他犯的是重罪  巴恩斯太太\N{\ren}What he did was a felony, Mrs. Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.78,1:09:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一共才1000美元\N{\ren}It was $1,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.00,1:09:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,像他这么大的孩子有一半在吸毒\N{\ren}Half the kids his age are on dope
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.66,1:09:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,向警察扔石子\N{\ren}throwing rocks at police
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.59,1:09:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都吓死我了\N{\ren}and they scared me to death
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.02,1:09:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为我的儿子犯了个小错误\N{\ren}because my son made a little mistake.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.82,1:09:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一个17岁的孩子需要吃饭...\N{\ren}Huh. A 17-year-old... boy has to eat
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.73,1:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,需要有个地方睡觉\N{\ren}has to have a place to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.24,1:09:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们理解  夫人\N{\ren}We understand, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.99,1:09:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有你儿子的照片吗?\N{\ren}Would you happen to have a picture of your son?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.73,1:09:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有  我有他的旧年册\N{\ren}Oh, yes. I have his old yearbook.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.80,1:09:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.39,1:09:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好  好  我们...\N{\ren}Okay, okay, we, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.33,1:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要给所有部门发电传\N{\ren}we need to send out an all-office teletype.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.42,1:09:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的嫌疑犯叫小弗兰克·阿巴戈内尔  17岁!\N{\ren}Our unsub's name is Frank Abagnale Jr., age 17.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.89,1:09:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰基没事吧?  他有麻烦了吗?\N{\ren}Is Frankie okay? Is he in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.17,1:09:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我得告诉你\N{\ren}Ma'am, I'm sorry to have to tell you:
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.43,1:09:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你儿子在伪造支票\N{\ren}Your son is forging checks.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.01,1:09:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,伪造支票?  等等!\N{\ren}Forging checks? Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.78,1:09:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们肯定能赔偿\N{\ren}I'm sure we can take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.30,1:09:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我在教堂做半日工\N{\ren}I am working part-time at the church now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.25,1:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我他欠多少  我还给你们\N{\ren}Just tell me how much he owes and I'll pay you back.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.79,1:10:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,到目前为止  约130万美元\N{\ren}so far, it's about $1.3 million.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.67,1:10:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,梅勒妮  你还好吧?\N{\ren}Hi, Melanie, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.70,1:10:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在室内时请用烟灰缸\N{\ren}When you're in the house, please, just use an ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.07,1:10:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  这奶油真好!\N{\ren}Frank, this fondue is so good!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.15,1:10:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  拿着\N{\ren}Great. Here, take this for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.88,1:10:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我喜欢摩埃特!\N{\ren}Ooh, good! I love Moet!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.50,1:10:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗?\N{\ren}Hey. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.06,1:10:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯  求你了!\N{\ren}James, James, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.12,1:10:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,离那音响远点  好吗?\N{\ren}Just stay away from the hi-fi system, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.46,1:10:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是卷轴到卷轴的  你不能那样进带\N{\ren}It's reel-to-reel. You can't wind it like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.30,1:10:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪  特里!\N{\ren}Christ! Terry!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.40,1:10:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是意大利的编织!  走路看着点\N{\ren}This is Italian knit! Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.71,1:10:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,只不过是件衬衫  伙计!\N{\ren}It's just a shirt, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.26,1:10:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克!  快过来!\N{\ren}Frank! Come quick!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.71,1:10:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,郎斯掉到谈话间里了!\N{\ren}Lance just fell into the conversation pit!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.72,1:11:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 你知道兰斯·埃坡巴姆在哪儿吗?\N{\ren}Excuse me, you know where Lance Applebaum is?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.30,1:11:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\ren}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.90,1:11:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这些瓶子一定要贴上标签!\N{\ren}These bottles need to be labeled when you pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.98,1:11:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这有多危险吗?\N{\ren}Do you understand how dangerous this is?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.40,1:11:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗?\N{\ren}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.47,1:11:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不要只是哭  要点头\N{\ren}Don't stand there crying, just nod your head
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.08,1:11:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我说你不再这样了\N{\ren}and tell me you won't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.48,1:11:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,擦干眼泪  去工作吧\N{\ren}Now dry up and get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.36,1:11:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱尔医生  布莱尔医生\N{\ren}Dr. Blair, Dr. Blair
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.68,1:11:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,薛伍德·布莱尔医生\N{\ren}Dr. Sherwood Blair.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.72,1:11:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧?\N{\ren}Hey, hey... you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.20,1:11:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫我去采血...\N{\ren}He told me to pick up the blood,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.86,1:11:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我就做了  但他从没告诉过我要贴标签\N{\ren}so I did, but he never told me to label it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.29,1:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  别哭了\N{\ren}Hey, it's okay. stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.79,1:11:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字?\N{\ren}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.35,1:11:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 布伦达  - 布伦达\N{\ren}-Brenda. -Brenda.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.00,1:11:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,布伦达  我不会介意它的\N{\ren}Brenda, I wouldn't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.29,1:11:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那些医生\N{\ren}You know, these doctors
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.82,1:11:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道  他们并不是什么都懂\N{\ren}you know, they don't know everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.50,1:11:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我第一周上班\N{\ren}It's my first week
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.50,1:11:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他们要解雇我了\N{\ren}and I think they're going to fire me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.76,1:11:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的  没有人会解雇你的\N{\ren}No, no, nobody's going to fire you, Brenda.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.94,1:11:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我打赌你会干得很好\N{\ren}I bet you're good at your job.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.68,1:11:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不会\N{\ren}No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.80,1:12:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我想如果我求你帮我查一下\N{\ren}Yeah, I bet if I asked you to check on the status
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.30,1:12:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友兰斯·埃坡巴姆的状况...\N{\ren}of my friend Lance Applebaum
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.42,1:12:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你会很快帮我做到的\N{\ren}that you could do that for me in a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.00,1:12:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,埃坡巴姆先生踝骨骨折\N{\ren}Mr. Applebaum fractured his ankle.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.86,1:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,阿什兰德医生在7号检查室给他治疗\N{\ren}Dr. Ashland is treating him in exam room seven.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.72,1:12:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你看?  没问题吧\N{\ren}You see that? No problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.19,1:12:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是急诊图表\N{\ren}This is the emergency chart.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.85,1:12:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看见那个蓝色的星了吗?\N{\ren}see that blue star there?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.41,1:12:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那表示病人已经被诊断\N{\ren}That means that the patient has been diagnosed.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.29,1:12:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,给他治疗后\N{\ren}And then, after he's been treated
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.20,1:12:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再在这里画个红圈  明白吗?\N{\ren}we put a red circle here, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.55,1:12:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得那些牙套怎么样?\N{\ren}How do you like those braces?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.56,1:12:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我看它们挺好\N{\ren}I guess they are all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.10,1:12:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我去年把我的摘下来了\N{\ren}I got mine off last year.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.10,1:12:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  我讨厌它们  只是里边的牙\N{\ren}Boy, I hated them. They were bottoms.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.50,1:12:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我还得戴我的护牙\N{\ren}You know, I still got to wear my mouth guard.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.58,1:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你的牙确实很好\N{\ren}You have really nice teeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.78,1:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\ren}Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.45,1:13:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你笑得很美\N{\ren}And you have a pretty smile.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.28,1:13:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我是认真的\N{\ren}No, I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.46,1:13:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我真觉得你戴牙套看上去挺好\N{\ren}I really think those braces look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.45,1:13:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\ren}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.00,1:13:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气\N{\ren}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.95,1:13:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 布伦达  - 什么?\N{\ren}- Brenda. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.85,1:13:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这医院有没有在招人?\N{\ren}Do you know if they're hiring here at the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.79,1:13:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定\N{\ren}I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.57,1:13:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你想干什么?\N{\ren}What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.83,1:13:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我是名医生\N{\ren}I'm a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.00,1:13:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的爸爸...\N{\ren}Dear Dad:
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.90,1:13:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定把原来的工作放下一段时间\N{\ren}I've decided to get off the road for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.40,1:13:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我找了个医院的夜班工作  遇到了一些不错的人\N{\ren}I've taken a night job at a hospital and met some really nice people.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.03,1:13:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉真好  每天晚上能\N{\ren}Feels good to have my feet on the ground
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.27,1:13:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,踏踏实实地睡在同一张床上\N{\ren}to wake up in the same bed every night.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.99,1:13:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,天知道  可能我还要找个人结婚\N{\ren}Who knows, maybe I'll even find someone to settle down with.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.66,1:13:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"哈佛医学院"...\N{\ren}Harvard Medical school...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.33,1:13:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,全班成绩前茅\N{\ren}top of your class.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.00,1:14:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"南加州儿童医院"\N{\ren}southern California Children's Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.81,1:14:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真是很吸引人的简历  考纳斯医生\N{\ren}Well, that's a pretty impressive resume, Dr. Conners
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.72,1:14:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不幸的是...  我需要的只是...\N{\ren}but unfortunately, uh... the only thing I need
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.53,1:14:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,一位夜班急诊室主管\N{\ren}is a... an emergency room supervisor
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.20,1:14:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,从半夜到早晨8点的\N{\ren}for my midnight to 8:00am shift
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.65,1:14:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一个照看6名实习生和20名护士的人\N{\ren}someone to baby-sit six interns and 20 nurses
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.82,1:14:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...\N{\ren}but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.10,1:14:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,说到底  我想你会感兴趣的\N{\ren}Hell, I doubt that, uh, you would be interested in that.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.58,1:14:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,过去... 我总是挑选自己的护士\N{\ren}Well, in the past they've always let me choose my own nurses.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.90,1:14:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,考纳利医生\N{\ren}Dr. Connelly?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.60,1:14:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哈里斯医生?  - 在\N{\ren}- Dr. Harris? - Present.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.30,1:14:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,阿什兰医生\N{\ren}Dr. Ashland?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.58,1:14:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,考纳斯医生...\N{\ren}Dr. Conners...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.75,1:14:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你每天晚上都要检查出勤吗?\N{\ren}You gonna take roll every night?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.72,1:14:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我要  阿什兰医生\N{\ren}Uh, yes, I will, Dr. Ashland,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.52,1:14:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要迟到了  我建议你带假条来\N{\ren}and if you're going to be late, I suggest you bring a note.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.30,1:14:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,巴斯曼小姐\N{\ren}Miss Basmann.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.72,1:14:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,梅斯小姐\N{\ren}Miss Mace.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.50,1:14:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,斯特朗小姐\N{\ren}Miss strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.40,1:14:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,到\N{\ren}Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.67,1:15:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,布朗护士\N{\ren}Nurse Brown.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.00,1:15:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 桑福德护士  - 到\N{\ren}-Nurse sanford? - Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.99,1:15:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,每4小时30毫克可待因\N{\ren}30 milligrams of codeine every four hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.45,1:15:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,每分钟60滴血浆  直到我们算出需要量\N{\ren}Run the plasma at 60 drops a minute until we calculate the fluid requirements.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.75,1:15:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你估计这烧伤的程度和面积有多少 基达尔?\N{\ren}What do you estimate the degree and extent of the burns, Kildare?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.92,1:15:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,2度和3度烧伤\N{\ren}second and third-degree burns
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.32,1:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,面积超过皮肤总面积的20%\N{\ren}over about 20 percent of the body surface.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.40,1:15:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你同意吗?  - 我同意\N{\ren}- Do you concur? - I concur.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.74,1:15:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,把他送到小儿科去吧\N{\ren}Let's get him up to Pediatrics.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.70,1:15:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好 布伦达  - 你好  考纳斯医生\N{\ren}- Hello, Brenda. - Hi, Dr. Conners.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.76,1:15:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你需要在这里签字  - 谢谢\N{\ren}- You need to sign these. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.70,1:15:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看我有什么变化吗?\N{\ren}Do you notice anything different about me, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.77,1:15:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你摘掉牙套了!  - 是的\N{\ren}-You got your braces off! -Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.39,1:15:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 过来  让我看看  - 我整晚都想让你看到!\N{\ren}- Come here. Let me see. - I've been trying to show you all night!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.13,1:15:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真不错  - 是吗?\N{\ren}- Wow. Good job. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.54,1:15:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,摘牙套时痛吗?  我当时感觉很怪异\N{\ren}so, did it hurt when they took them off? Mine felt so weird after.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.15,1:15:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我总是用舌头磨牙  控制不住!\N{\ren}Mm, I keep rubbing my tongue over them. I can't stop. They're so slippery.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.15,1:16:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 感觉很好  是吗?  - 是的  感觉好极了\N{\ren}- It feels good, though, doesn't it? - Yeah, it feels incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.59,1:16:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,天...!\N{\ren}Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.88,1:16:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\ren}I'm... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.30,1:16:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,考纳斯医生  请到急诊室\N{\ren}Dr. Conners to the ER.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.82,1:16:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你不去吗?\N{\ren}shouldn't you go?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.01,1:16:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不去\N{\ren}No. No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.21,1:16:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,急诊病房有位医生  我们继续\N{\ren}They have a staff doctor in the emergency ward. We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.99,1:16:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他要是正在手术怎么办?\N{\ren}What... what if he's in surgery?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.60,1:16:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的认为我得去?\N{\ren}Do you really think I have to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.10,1:16:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里边  考纳斯医生\N{\ren}Oh. In here, Dr. Conners.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.67,1:17:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们  是什么问题?\N{\ren}Gentlemen, what, uh... what seems to be the problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.90,1:17:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,脚踏车意外\N{\ren}Bicycle accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.43,1:17:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,膝盖骨下大约13厘米处胫骨骨折\N{\ren}Fractured tibia about five inches below the patella.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.88,1:17:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哈里斯医生  - 嗯?\N{\ren}-Dr. Harris. - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.59,1:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你同意吗?\N{\ren}Do you concur?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.00,1:17:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,同意什么  先生?\N{\ren}C... Concur with what, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.65,1:17:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,同意阿什兰医生刚才说的\N{\ren}With what Dr. Ashland just said.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.67,1:17:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你同意吗?\N{\ren}Do you... Do you concur?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.38,1:17:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是个脚踏车意外\N{\ren}Uh... well, it was a bicycle accident.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.75,1:17:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子说的\N{\ren}Um, the boy told us.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.68,1:17:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你同意?\N{\ren}so you concur?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.18,1:17:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 同意?  - 我们应该给他照X光\N{\ren}- Concur? Uh... - I think we should take an X ray,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.41,1:17:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,缝合伤口  再给他打上石膏\N{\ren}then stitch him up and put him in a walking cast.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.30,1:17:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  阿什兰医生  很好\N{\ren}That's very good, Dr. Ashland. Very good.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.09,1:17:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我看  你们好像不太需要我\N{\ren}Well, you don't seem to have much need for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.60,1:17:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\ren}Carry on.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.00,1:17:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我搞错了  是不是?\N{\ren}I blew it, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.80,1:18:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么没说同意呢?\N{\ren}Why didn't I concur?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.20,1:18:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,请接219分机\N{\ren}Dr.Henning, call extension 219.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.79,1:18:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,接219分机\N{\ren}Dr.Henning, extension 219.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.28,1:18:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,请随便!\N{\ren}Make yourself at home!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.56,1:18:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老弗兰克·阿巴戈内尔\N{\ren}Frank Abagnale sr.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.21,1:18:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是警察\N{\ren}You're not a cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.26,1:18:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局  特工汉莱提\N{\ren}special Agent Handratty, FBI.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.07,1:18:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是警察\N{\ren}You're not a cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.12,1:18:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的房东说你不是警察\N{\ren}My landlord said you were not a cop.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.68,1:18:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要拘捕我  我想换件衣服\N{\ren}Well, if you're going to arrest me I'd like to put on a different suit
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.76,1:18:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果可以的话  - 我不是来拘捕你的\N{\ren}- if that's okay with you. - No, no, I'm not here to arrest you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.92,1:18:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在抓你儿子  他有麻烦了\N{\ren}I'm looking for your son. He's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.31,1:18:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他在哪里吗?\N{\ren}Do you know where he is?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.30,1:18:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我告诉你他在哪里\N{\ren}If I tell you where he is
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.58,1:18:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你能保证不告诉她妈吗?\N{\ren}will you promise not to tell his mother?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.90,1:18:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,能\N{\ren}sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.95,1:18:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克做了个假身份证\N{\ren}Frank made up a fake I.D.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.94,1:19:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,还参加海军了\N{\ren}and enlisted in the Marine Corps.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.42,1:19:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在在越南\N{\ren}He's over in Vietnam right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.51,1:19:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子现在在地球那头...\N{\ren}That kid is halfway around the world
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.74,1:19:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在该死的丛林里爬行\N{\ren}crawling through the damn jungle
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.80,1:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,跟共产党打仗  所以...\N{\ren}fighting the Communists, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.26,1:19:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,请你  不要到我家来  还说我儿子是罪犯\N{\ren}please, don't come to my home and call my boy a criminal
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.94,1:19:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 因为这孩子更有出息  - 我没说他是罪犯\N{\ren}- because that kid has more guts... - I never said he was a criminal, Mr. Abagnale.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.84,1:19:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我说他有麻烦了\N{\ren}I said he was in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.69,1:19:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想给我打电话谈谈  这是我电话\N{\ren}If you'd like to give me a call and talk, here's my number.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.40,1:19:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定没有孩子吧?\N{\ren}You're not a father, are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.60,1:19:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\ren}Pardon me?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.89,1:19:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你也是名父亲的话  你就会明白\N{\ren}If you were a father, you'd know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.00,1:19:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远不会对我的儿子失望\N{\ren}I would never give up my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.80,1:19:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也永远不会放弃我的儿子\N{\ren}I would never give up my son.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.50,1:19:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  先生  我理解\N{\ren}Yes, sir. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.61,1:19:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,肖恩  记下这个...\N{\ren}Sean, Sean, now get this:
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.79,1:19:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"河湾公寓\N{\ren}"Riverbend Apartments
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.30,1:20:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,乔治亚州  亚特兰大市  兰德欧沃街415号"\N{\ren}415 Landover, Atlanta, Georgia."
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.97,1:20:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,乔治亚州  亚特兰大市\N{\ren}Atlanta, Georgia.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.43,1:20:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我在去机场的路上\N{\ren}Yeah, I'm on my way to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.16,1:20:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,4小时后和小组会合  再见\N{\ren}I'll meet the team in, uh, in four hours. Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.57,1:20:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  没关系的\N{\ren}Come on, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.10,1:20:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不必哭\N{\ren}You don't have to cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.00,1:20:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起!\N{\ren}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.95,1:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真对不起  弗兰克!\N{\ren}I'm so sorry, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.86,1:20:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能这么做\N{\ren}I can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.57,1:20:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,布伦达  听我说\N{\ren}Brenda, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.96,1:20:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎你是处女\N{\ren}I don't care if you're a virgin, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.33,1:20:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以等\N{\ren}Really, I can wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.77,1:20:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是处女\N{\ren}I'm not a virgin.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.75,1:20:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我2年前做了堕胎手术\N{\ren}I had an abortion two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.71,1:20:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我父母找朋友做的\N{\ren}My parents had a friend do it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.31,1:20:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一个和我父亲一起打高尔夫的人\N{\ren}a man that my father plays golf with.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.67,1:20:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,当我刚恢复好  他们就把我踢出了家门\N{\ren}And then, when I got better, they kicked me out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.07,1:20:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我堕过胎  不再是他们的女儿了!\N{\ren}I had an abortion and I wasn't their daughter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.51,1:20:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\ren}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.52,1:20:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要生我的气\N{\ren}Please don't be mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.17,1:21:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了  请不要生我的气\N{\ren}Please, please, don't be mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.37,1:21:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不生气\N{\ren}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.52,1:21:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要生我的气\N{\ren}Please don't be mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.83,1:21:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果... 我同你父母谈谈怎样?\N{\ren}shh. Now... what if... what if I spoke to your parents, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.00,1:21:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也许能理顺关系\N{\ren}May-Maybe I can straighten things out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.30,1:21:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在求他们  但他们还是不让我回家\N{\ren}Well, I ask them all the time but they said I still can't come home.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.39,1:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸爸是律师\N{\ren}And my daddy's... a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.02,1:21:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,布伦达?\N{\ren}Brenda...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.57,1:21:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你跟一位医生订婚会怎样?\N{\ren}what if you were engaged to a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.08,1:21:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那样会不会改变什么?\N{\ren}Will that change anything?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.45,1:21:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\ren}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.50,1:21:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我去你父母那里...\N{\ren}What if I went to your parents...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.20,1:21:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,同你父亲谈谈...\N{\ren}and I spoke to your father...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.87,1:21:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,求他同意把你嫁给我\N{\ren}and I asked permission to marry you?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.40,1:22:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是空的\N{\ren}It's empty.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.63,1:22:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人\N{\ren}Nobody here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.62,1:22:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,考纳斯医生  你是路德教徒吗?\N{\ren}Dr. Conners, are you Lutheran?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.66,1:22:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是  我是路德教徒  \N{\ren}Yes, I-I am a Lutheran,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.57,1:22:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但是请叫我弗兰克\N{\ren}but, please, call me Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.02,1:22:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  你来祈祷好吗?\N{\ren}Frank, would you like to say grace?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.10,1:22:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你觉得不自在\N{\ren}Unless you're not comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.80,1:22:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对可以\N{\ren}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.39,1:23:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,两只老鼠掉进奶油桶里\N{\ren}Two little mice fell into a bucket of cream.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.68,1:23:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,第一只老鼠很快放弃  被淹死了...\N{\ren}The first mouse quickly gave up and drowned
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.77,1:23:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是第二只老鼠拼命努力\N{\ren}but the second mouse, he struggled so hard
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.94,1:23:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,把奶油搅拌成黄油\N{\ren}that he eventually churned that cream into butter
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.95,1:23:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它走了出来\N{\ren}and he walked out.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.32,1:23:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿门  - 阿门\N{\ren}-Amen. -Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.21,1:23:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,阿门  那很美...\N{\ren}Amen. Oh, that was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.10,1:23:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,老鼠把奶油搅拌成了黄油\N{\ren}The mouse, he churned that cream into butter.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.67,1:23:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\ren}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.23,1:23:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那很不错  - 谢谢\N{\ren}- That's pretty good. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.70,1:23:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有决定想在新奥尔良的...\N{\ren}Frank, have you decided which hospital...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.59,1:23:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哪一家医院工作?\N{\ren}you want to work at here in New Orleans?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.50,1:23:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,说实在的\N{\ren}Well, um, to be quite honest
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.78,1:23:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我在考虑回到法律这行\N{\ren}I'm thinking about getting back into law.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.03,1:23:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊!\N{\ren}Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.50,1:23:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你是医生还是律师?\N{\ren}Are you a doctor or a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.00,1:23:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我去医学院之前 在加州通过了律师考试\N{\ren}Before I went to medical school, I passed the bar in California.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.35,1:23:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我实习了一年\N{\ren}I practiced law for one year
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.67,1:23:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,后来我决定为什么不试试当个儿科医生呢?\N{\ren}then I decided why not try my hand at pediatrics?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.95,1:24:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你真让人惊奇\N{\ren}You're just full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.10,1:24:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\ren}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.69,1:24:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐  医生和律师\N{\ren}Oh, my. A doctor and a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.28,1:24:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,布伦达中大奖了\N{\ren}Well, I'd say that Brenda hit the jackpot.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.39,1:24:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪儿上的法律学校?\N{\ren}Where did you go to law school?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.90,1:24:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,伯克利\N{\ren}Uh, Berkeley.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.68,1:24:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,伯克利  伯克利  天啊!\N{\ren}Berkley, Berkley. Oh, my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.12,1:24:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是你上学的地方吗  爸?\N{\ren}Isn't that where you went, Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.16,1:24:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克可以帮你工作\N{\ren}Maybe Frank could come work for you, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.62,1:24:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是说找助理起诉员有多难\N{\ren}You're always saying how hard it is to find Assistant Prosecutors.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.55,1:24:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他行吗  爸爸?  他行吗  求你了?\N{\ren}Could he, Daddy? Could he, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.38,1:24:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他能为你工作吗?  求你了?\N{\ren}Could he come work with you, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.89,1:24:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你在伯克利念书时  \N{\ren}Was that snake Hollingsworth still teaching there
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.44,1:24:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那个狡猾的霍灵斯沃还在教学吗?\N{\ren}when you went through Berkley?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.07,1:24:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,霍灵斯沃\N{\ren}Hollingsworth.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.94,1:24:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  坏脾气的老霍灵斯沃  对吗?\N{\ren}Yes. Grumpy old Hollingsworth, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.61,1:24:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,脾气更坏了\N{\ren}I tell you. Meaner than ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.41,1:24:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还有他的狗呢?\N{\ren}And that dog of his?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.40,1:24:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我  弗兰克  他的狗叫什么名字?\N{\ren}Tell me, Frank, what was the name of his little dog?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.20,1:24:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\ren}I'm sorry. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.95,1:25:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,狗死了\N{\ren}The dog was dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.11,1:25:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不幸\N{\ren}How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.42,1:25:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\ren}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.00,1:25:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一个医生  律师  路德教徒...\N{\ren}A doctor, a lawyer, a Lutheran...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.40,1:25:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  你究竟是什么  弗兰克?\N{\ren}so what are you, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.60,1:25:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你要跟我女儿结婚...\N{\ren}'Cause I think you're about to ask for my daughter's hand in marriage
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.87,1:25:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我有权利知道\N{\ren}and I have a right to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.00,1:25:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,知道什么  先生?\N{\ren}Know what, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.20,1:25:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,事实\N{\ren}The truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.90,1:26:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我事实  弗兰克\N{\ren}Tell me the truth, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.95,1:26:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这儿做什么?\N{\ren}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.08,1:26:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,像你这样的人在和布伦达做什么?\N{\ren}What is a man like you doing with Brenda?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.52,1:26:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想要我的祝福\N{\ren}If you want my blessing
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.25,1:26:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想要我的女儿...\N{\ren}if you want my daughter
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.51,1:26:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我想现在就听你说说\N{\ren}I'd like to hear it from you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.23,1:26:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,事实是  先生...\N{\ren}The truth is, sir, that...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.95,1:26:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,事实就是...\N{\ren}The truth is that...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.99,1:26:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是医生  也不是律师\N{\ren}I'm not a doctor, I'm not a lawyer...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.68,1:26:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是飞行员\N{\ren}I'm not an airline pilot.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.47,1:26:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都不是\N{\ren}I'm... I'm nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.35,1:26:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是个爱你女儿的孩子\N{\ren}I'm-I'm-I'm just a kid who's in love with your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.29,1:26:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不对\N{\ren}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.65,1:27:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你是什么吗?\N{\ren}You know what you are?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.11,1:27:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个浪漫的人\N{\ren}You're a romantic.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.13,1:27:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没有我们爱的女人  像我们这样的男人什么都不是\N{\ren}Men like us are nothing without the women we love.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.23,1:27:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须承认  我也为有这样愚蠢的内疚怪念头\N{\ren}I must confess, I'm guilty of the same foolish whimsy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.95,1:27:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,五次约会后我向卡罗尔求婚...\N{\ren}I proposed to Carol after five dates
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.15,1:27:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,口袋空空  一文不名\N{\ren}with two nickels in my pockets and holes in my shoes
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.94,1:27:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我知道她就是那个我要找的\N{\ren}because I knew she was the one.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.75,1:27:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,继续向前  弗兰克\N{\ren}so go ahead, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.36,1:27:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不要害怕\N{\ren}Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.46,1:27:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,提出你想跟我提的吧\N{\ren}Ask the question you came here to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.22,1:27:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,先生...\N{\ren}sir, uh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.81,1:27:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我得做什么?\N{\ren}w-what would I have to do
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.37,1:27:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要想在新奥尔良当律师?\N{\ren}to take the bar here in New Orleans?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.94,1:27:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不  别的问题\N{\ren}No, the... the other question.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.04,1:27:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,穿过那门就是\N{\ren}Right through that door.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.40,1:27:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运  考纳斯先生\N{\ren}Good luck, Mr. Conners.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.70,1:28:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\ren}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.40,1:28:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}1969年12月26日
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.20,1:28:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克\N{\ren}Hey, Frank...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.93,1:28:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我一直没明白的是什么吗?\N{\ren}you know what I could never figure out?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.17,1:28:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么骗过律师考试的?\N{\ren}How did you cheat on the bar exam in Louisiana?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.01,1:28:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么区别?\N{\ren}Why? What's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.00,1:28:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有人替你考试的  有吗?\N{\ren}someone else took the test for you, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.48,1:28:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔  我要被长时间地关在监狱里\N{\ren}Carl, I'm going to prison for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.31,1:28:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,说真的  知不知道有什么区别?\N{\ren}seriously, what's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.30,1:28:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就是个简单的问题\N{\ren}It's a simple question.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.23,1:28:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃那小酶吗?\N{\ren}Are you going to eat that eclair?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.71,1:28:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我留着等会儿吃\N{\ren}Yeah. I'm saving it for later.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.19,1:28:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,或者你想分点给我?\N{\ren}Well, you want to split it with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.32,1:28:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不想\N{\ren}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.80,1:28:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,把小酶给我一半我就告诉你\N{\ren}Give me half that eclair and I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.19,1:28:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我早晚会想出来的\N{\ren}I'm going to figure it out sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.23,1:29:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你在菲利浦·利戈比手下工作  负责企业法务\N{\ren}You'll be working under Phillip Rigby in corporate law.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.50,1:29:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不搬进来  布置一下办公桌?\N{\ren}Why don't you settle in, organize your desk?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.58,1:29:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\ren}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.68,1:29:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们12点30分与首席检察官和\N{\ren}We're having lunch at 12:30 with the Attorney General
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.60,1:29:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克森州长共进午餐\N{\ren}and Governor McKeithen.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.63,1:29:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他本人  - 州长!\N{\ren}- Himself. - The Governor.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.43,1:29:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们拼写得正确吗?\N{\ren}Did we spell it right?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.20,1:29:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,非常对\N{\ren}You sure did.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.80,1:29:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  \N{\ren}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.97,1:29:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢  先生  - 欢迎你的加入\N{\ren}- Thank you, sir. - Welcome aboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.90,1:29:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看这张照片  斯图尔特先生\N{\ren}Look at this photograph, Mr. Stewart.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.99,1:29:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这是张普林提斯约克的照片\N{\ren}It's a photograph of Prentice York
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.13,1:29:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在那他们发现他死了\N{\ren}where they found him, dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.54,1:29:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是照片的局部放大\N{\ren}Now, here is an enlargement of part of that photograph.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.64,1:29:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一张被告在作废支票上的签名照片\N{\ren}This is a photograph of the defendant's signature on a canceled check.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.56,1:29:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这是同一个签名的局部放大\N{\ren}Now, here is an enlargement of that same signature
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.31,1:29:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,与...\N{\ren}which matches
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.58,1:29:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他写给西蒙太太的信上的签名相吻合\N{\ren}the signature on the letters that he wrote to Mrs. Simon
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.67,1:30:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这就说明了某种可能性...\N{\ren}which discuss the possibility
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.49,1:30:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,说明...  他在路易斯安娜州行骗\N{\ren}of defrauding the great state of Louisiana.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.12,1:30:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人  陪审团的女士们  先生们...\N{\ren}Your Honor, ladies and gentlemen of the jury
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.00,1:30:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是不可辩驳的证据\N{\ren}this is irrefutable evidence
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.57,1:30:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,说明被告确实在说谎\N{\ren}that the defendant is, in fact, lying.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.06,1:30:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,考纳斯先生  这是预审\N{\ren}Mr. Conners, this is a preliminary hearing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.00,1:30:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没有被告\N{\ren}There is no... defendant.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.62,1:30:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有陪审团\N{\ren}There is no... jury.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.31,1:30:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我\N{\ren}It's just me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.90,1:30:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子...\N{\ren}son...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.40,1:30:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底怎么了?\N{\ren}what in the hell is wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.36,1:30:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是米驰吗?\N{\ren}Is that Mitch?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.00,1:30:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,罗杰!  是米驰!\N{\ren}Roger! It's Mitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.81,1:30:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是米驰!\N{\ren}Oh, my, I lost all track of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.99,1:30:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,作为今晚"跟着唱"现场嘉宾...\N{\ren}As studio guests for the sing-along tonight
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.10,1:30:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们邀请了圣莫尼卡教堂的 儿童合唱组\N{\ren}we have the children's choir of st. Monica's Church
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.11,1:30:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来自纽约城\N{\ren}in New York City.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.97,1:30:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,纽约城你能加入他们!\N{\ren}Won't you join them and the gang
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.30,1:30:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,为爱尔兰唱几首歌吗?  大家一起\N{\ren}in a few songs for the Irish? Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.06,1:30:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有人看见过凯莉吗?\N{\ren}Has anybody here seen Kelly?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.78,1:31:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有人看见过凯莉吗?\N{\ren}Has anybody here seen Kelly?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.37,1:32:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你来干什么?\N{\ren}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.77,1:32:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我来看你\N{\ren}I... I-I came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.02,1:32:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你穿成这样干什么?\N{\ren}What are you doing dressed like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.87,1:32:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我找了份政府工作\N{\ren}I took a job. A government job.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.20,1:32:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我在做什么吗?\N{\ren}You see what I'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.68,1:32:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有个好律师?\N{\ren}Do you have a good lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.46,1:32:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在也算是个律师\N{\ren}Well... I sort of am a lawyer now.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.13,1:32:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看这封信  税务局想要更多\N{\ren}Look at this letter. The IRs wants more.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.65,1:32:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他们达成个协议  我交2项罚金\N{\ren}I had a deal with them: two penalties.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.43,1:33:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们吃了蛋糕  现在还想要掉下的渣子\N{\ren}They ate the cake, now they want the crumbs.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.93,1:33:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我想起诉他们\N{\ren}I want to sue them.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.60,1:33:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他们想要渣子\N{\ren}Now they want the crumbs.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.86,1:33:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们...  来  坐下\N{\ren}They... Here, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.01,1:33:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们试图吓唬我\N{\ren}They're trying to scare me, intimidate me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.40,1:33:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗?\N{\ren}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.70,1:33:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,知道什么?  我要让他们追逐我...\N{\ren}You know what? I'll make them chase me...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.60,1:33:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,用他们的余生!\N{\ren}for the rest of their lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.41,1:33:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴看见你  爸爸\N{\ren}Hey, it's great to see you, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.21,1:33:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下  我想给你看样东西\N{\ren}Listen, sit down, I... I want to show you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.77,1:33:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我来是要给你这个\N{\ren}I came here to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.15,1:33:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的订婚舞会邀请函\N{\ren}It's an invitation to an engagement party.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.56,1:33:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  我要结婚了\N{\ren}Daddy, I'm getting married.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.48,1:33:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你能相信我要结婚了吗?\N{\ren}Can you believe that? I'm getting married.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.30,1:33:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在什么都不用担心了\N{\ren}You don't need to worry about anything now, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.87,1:33:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我要有辆崭新的卡迪拉克\N{\ren}Listen, I'm getting a brand-new Cadillac.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.42,1:33:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要有栋6万美元的房子...\N{\ren}I'm getting a $60,000 house.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.29,1:33:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我全得回来了\N{\ren}I'm-I'm getting it all back.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.31,1:34:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的珠宝  毛皮...\N{\ren}All-All the jewelry, all the furs, everything, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.35,1:34:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们拿走的每一样东西  我都要得回来\N{\ren}Everything they took from us, I'm going to get it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.81,1:34:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,妈看见你穿成这样了吗?\N{\ren}Now...has Ma seen you dressed like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.40,1:34:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对  她回来取过几个箱子\N{\ren}Yeah, she came to pick up some boxes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.32,1:34:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好  你知道为什么?\N{\ren}That's okay, that's okay, you know why?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.01,1:34:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她要跟我们一起去参加婚礼\N{\ren}'Cause she... she's going to the wedding with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.41,1:34:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我要给你穿套全新的衣服\N{\ren}I'm going to get you a brand-new suit, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.53,1:34:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要给你穿套全新的衣服\N{\ren}I'm getting you a brand-new suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.60,1:34:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,一套曼哈顿之鹰  带3颗黑色珍珠纽扣\N{\ren}One of those Manhattan Eagle, three-button, black pearl suits.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.73,1:34:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你会帅极了\N{\ren}You'll look great.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.28,1:34:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那些是不错  但她不会见我的\N{\ren}Those are nice. Yeah. she won't see me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.48,1:34:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有试着给她打电话?\N{\ren}Well, have you tried to call her?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.58,1:34:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你现在不给她打电话呢?\N{\ren}Why don't... why don't you call her right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.21,1:34:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  为什么你现在不给她打电话呢?\N{\ren}Dad, why don't you call her right now? Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.74,1:34:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,爸  给她打电话  为了我打\N{\ren}Dad, just call her. Call her for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.33,1:34:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,打给她  告诉她...\N{\ren}You call her, and you tell her
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.10,1:34:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我有2张头等仓机票  去看她儿子的婚礼...\N{\ren}I have two first-class tickets to go see her son's wedding...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.15,1:34:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你母亲现在和杰克·巴恩斯结婚了\N{\ren}Your mother's married now, to my friend Jack Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.72,1:34:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在长岛有套房子\N{\ren}They have a house in Long Island.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.50,1:34:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦调查局来找过我\N{\ren}I had an FBI agent come see me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.30,1:34:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你能躲着他们  儿子\N{\ren}You got their number, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.40,1:34:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙很凶\N{\ren}The guy looked scared.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.10,1:35:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,美国政府  亲爱的  吓得不敢照面\N{\ren}The United states government, champ, running for the hills.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.55,1:35:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,乒!  一步登天!\N{\ren}Pow! To the moon!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.32,1:35:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,都结束了\N{\ren}Dad... it's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.60,1:35:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我要洗手不干了\N{\ren}I'm going to stop now.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.40,1:35:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你已经...\N{\ren}But y-you've...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.20,1:35:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他们永远也抓不住你\N{\ren}They're never going to catch you, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.94,1:35:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她不该那样做!  - 坐下来好吗?\N{\ren}- Dad, she wouldn't do that. - Why won't you sit down?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.31,1:35:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,她为什么那样做\N{\ren}Why would she do that to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.80,1:35:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,过来坐下  喝一杯\N{\ren}Come on, sit with me. Have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.44,1:35:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你父亲\N{\ren}I'm your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.99,1:35:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那叫我住手吧\N{\ren}Then ask me to stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.60,1:35:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那么叫我住手吧\N{\ren}Then ask me to stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.48,1:35:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能停\N{\ren}You can't stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.57,1:35:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿?\N{\ren}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.44,1:35:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  你要去哪儿?\N{\ren}Come on, Frank, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.00,1:35:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿?\N{\ren}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.44,1:35:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你今晚去哪儿?\N{\ren}Where are you going tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.41,1:35:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你今晚要去什么奇异的地方?\N{\ren}someplace exotic? Where are you going tonight?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:57.69,1:35:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,塔西提岛?  夏威夷?\N{\ren}Tahiti, Hawaii?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.66,1:36:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这是汉莱提\N{\ren}This is Handratty.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.62,1:36:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  卡尔\N{\ren}Hello, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.74,1:36:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐\N{\ren}Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.77,1:36:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗  考纳斯医生?\N{\ren}How are you, Dr. Conners?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.18,1:36:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经有几个月不当考纳斯医生了\N{\ren}Carl, I haven't been Dr. Conners for months now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.61,1:36:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,平安夜我坐在办公室\N{\ren}Well... I'm sitting here in my office on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.55,1:36:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你想干什么?\N{\ren}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.60,1:36:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\ren}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.80,1:36:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想结束这一切\N{\ren}I want it to be over.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.08,1:37:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我想结束这一切  因为我要结婚了\N{\ren}Uh... I want it to be over. I'm getting married.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.69,1:37:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,想安顿下来\N{\ren}You know, I'm settling down.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.50,1:37:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你偷了差不多4百万美元\N{\ren}You've stolen almost $4 million.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.76,1:37:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你想我们能把这作为结婚礼物给你?\N{\ren}You think we can just call that a wedding present?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.17,1:37:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是件你能躲开的事\N{\ren}Nah, this isn't something you get to walk away from, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.56,1:37:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想休战  - 没有休战\N{\ren}- I want to call a truce. - No truce.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.37,1:37:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你会被抓住  投入监狱\N{\ren}You will be caught, you will go to prison.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.82,1:37:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为后果会是怎样的?\N{\ren}Where did you think this was going?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.00,1:37:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,请放我一马  卡尔\N{\ren}Please leave me alone, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.27,1:37:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\ren}Please?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.85,1:37:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我就快抓住你了  不是吗?\N{\ren}I'm getting close, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.33,1:37:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我接近了所以你害怕了\N{\ren}You're scared because I'm getting close.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.91,1:37:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道...  你在什里夫伯特租了辆车\N{\ren}I know you... you rented that car in shreveport
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.21,1:37:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,住在查尔斯湖的一家旅馆\N{\ren}and you stayed in that hotel on Lake Charles.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.25,1:37:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你想跑  尽管去吧\N{\ren}You want to run, be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.33,1:37:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你的支票可不像你那么会说谎\N{\ren}Your checks don't lie as well as you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.74,1:37:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要追我了\N{\ren}stop chasing me.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.53,1:37:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能停\N{\ren}I can't stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.29,1:37:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的工作\N{\ren}It's my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.91,1:37:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  卡尔\N{\ren}It's okay, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.00,1:37:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想我该问一下\N{\ren}I just thought I'd ask, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.41,1:37:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐\N{\ren}Hey. Merry Christmas, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.70,1:38:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱我的工作\N{\ren}I love my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.39,1:38:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\ren}All right...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.09,1:38:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们找来所有的报纸...\N{\ren}let's get every newspaper we can
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.61,1:38:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,最近两个月的路易斯安娜州的所有报纸\N{\ren}every newspaper in Louisiana for the last two months.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.15,1:38:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要找什么?\N{\ren}What are we looking for?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.13,1:38:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,结婚声明  以考纳斯的名字\N{\ren}Engagement announcements, name of Conners.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.87,1:38:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,考纳斯?  得了  这孩子现在应该已经...\N{\ren}Conners?! Come on, Carl, the kid would've
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.80,1:38:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,已经改名了\N{\ren}changed his name by now.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.93,1:38:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能改\N{\ren}Mm-mm. He can't change it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.62,1:38:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她认为他是考纳斯\N{\ren}she thinks he's Conners.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.40,1:38:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他丢了名字  就丢了她\N{\ren}If he loses the name, he loses the girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.77,1:38:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 恭喜!  - 玩得好吗?\N{\ren}-Congratulations. - You having a good time?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.30,1:38:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,继续跳舞\N{\ren}Keep dancing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.40,1:38:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你也一样  谢谢\N{\ren}Oh, me too. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.41,1:38:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我去一下洗手间\N{\ren}I'm going to, uh, the little boys' room.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.31,1:38:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的  - 好的\N{\ren}-Okay. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.54,1:38:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快点回来\N{\ren}Hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.31,1:39:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好\N{\ren}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.06,1:39:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我是联邦调查局的汉莱提特工\N{\ren}I'm Agent Handratty with the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.27,1:39:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想和主人谈话\N{\ren}We'd like to have a few quiet words
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.44,1:39:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果方便的话  - 我去找他\N{\ren}- with your host, if possible. - I'll get him.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.48,1:39:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就在那儿  先生\N{\ren}Right over there, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.00,1:39:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你好  罗杰   - 你好\N{\ren}-Hi, Roger. How are you? -Hi, Vin.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.79,1:39:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上好  我是罗杰·斯特朗\N{\ren}Good evening, gentlemen. I'm Roger strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.73,1:39:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔·汉莱提  联邦调查局的\N{\ren}Carl Handratty, FBI.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.31,1:39:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是阿姆德斯基和福克斯特工\N{\ren}This is Agents Amdursky and Fox.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.20,1:39:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉闯到你的舞会\N{\ren}sorry to crash your party, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.58,1:39:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  我能为你做什么?\N{\ren}Not at all. What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.10,1:39:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不太麻烦  我想见新郎\N{\ren}If it's not too much trouble, I'd like to meet the groom.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.14,1:39:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗?\N{\ren}Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.23,1:39:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克!  弗兰克!\N{\ren}Frank! Frank!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.72,1:39:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你能拿一下这些支票吗?\N{\ren}Can you hold all these?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.70,1:39:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  来这边\N{\ren}Yeah. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.80,1:39:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这些支票是我父亲的朋友送的\N{\ren}They're checks. They're from my dad's friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.21,1:39:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是送给我们用来开始新生活...\N{\ren}They're for us, so we can start a new life... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.98,1:39:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么?  怎么了?\N{\ren}What are you doing? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.34,1:39:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们得离开  - 什么?!\N{\ren}- We have to leave. - What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.55,1:39:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 布伦达  你爱我  是吧?  - 是的\N{\ren}- Brenda, you love me, right? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.86,1:39:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是说  无论怎样你都会爱我  - 是的\N{\ren}- I mean, you'd love me no matter what. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.75,1:39:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说  无论我生病\N{\ren}I mean, you'd love me
Dialogue: 0,1:39:59.60,1:40:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还是贫穷  或者甚至...\N{\ren}whether I was sick or whether I was poor
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.25,1:40:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有另外一个名字  你都会爱我\N{\ren}or even if I had a different name.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.20,1:40:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  你从哪儿弄来的那些钱?\N{\ren}Frank, where'd you get all that money?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.79,1:40:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,布伦达  听我说   名字并不重要  对吗\N{\ren}Brenda, listen. A name, right? A name, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.09,1:40:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫弗兰克·考纳斯  对吧?\N{\ren}My name is Frank Conners, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.47,1:40:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是跟你一起时用的名字  - 对\N{\ren}- That's who I am with you. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.16,1:40:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们都有秘密  有时旅行时...\N{\ren}But-but we all have secrets. You know, sometimes when I travel
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.25,1:40:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我用弗兰克·泰勒这名字  这是我的秘密\N{\ren}I use the name Frank Taylor. That-That's my secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.51,1:40:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 弗兰克·泰勒?  - 是的  弗兰克·布莱克\N{\ren}-Frank Taylor?! -Yeah, Frank Taylor, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.41,1:40:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 弗兰克·布莱克  - 弗兰克·布莱克?!\N{\ren}-Frank Black. -Frank Black?!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.17,1:40:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的  这没关系  - 你为什么说这些?\N{\ren}- Yeah, it doesn't matter. - Why are you saying all this?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.38,1:40:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,布伦达  我不想再跟你说谎\N{\ren}Brenda... Brenda, I don't want to lie to you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.82,1:40:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗?  我不是医生\N{\ren}All right? I'm not a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.54,1:40:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,从来没上过医学院\N{\ren}I never went to medical school.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.78,1:40:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是律师  不是哈佛毕业生  也不是路德教徒\N{\ren}I'm not a lawyer or a Harvard graduate or a Lutheran.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.53,1:40:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,布伦达  我1年半前从家里跑出来\N{\ren}Brenda, I ran away from home a year and a half ago
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.91,1:40:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那时16岁时\N{\ren}when I was 16.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.17,1:40:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克...\N{\ren}Frank...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.01,1:40:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克?\N{\ren}Frank?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.38,1:40:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是路德教徒?\N{\ren}You're not a Lutheran?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.41,1:40:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,布伦达  看见这些钱了吗?\N{\ren}Brenda... you see all this money?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:45.94,1:40:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看见这些钱了吗?  我还有\N{\ren}You see all this money? I have more.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.98,1:40:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有更多\N{\ren}I have plenty more.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.69,1:40:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我有的是钱\N{\ren}I have enough money
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.70,1:40:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,足够我们两个下半辈子用了\N{\ren}to last us for the rest of our lives
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.69,1:40:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\ren}Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.17,1:40:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别逗我了!\N{\ren}Frank, stop teasing me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.35,1:41:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你是弗兰克·考纳斯  28岁\N{\ren}You're Frank Conners. You're Frank Conners, and you're 28 years old and...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.36,1:41:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 布伦达  - 你为什么对我说谎?\N{\ren}- Brenda... - Why would you lie to me?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.13,1:41:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 布伦达  布伦达...   - 我想知道你的名字\N{\ren}-Brenda  Brenda... - I want to know your name.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.82,1:41:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 听我说  布伦达  - 告诉我你的名字\N{\ren}-Listen to me, Brenda. -Tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.34,1:41:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以住在任何想住的地方\N{\ren}We can live anywhere we want
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.91,1:41:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你得信任我  布伦达\N{\ren}but you have to trust me, Brenda.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.62,1:41:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你信任我吗?  - 是的\N{\ren}- Do you trust me? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.02,1:41:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你爱我吗  布伦达?  - 我爱你\N{\ren}- Do you love me, Brenda? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.57,1:41:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你爱我?  - 我爱你\N{\ren}- You love me? - I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.90,1:41:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,打断一下  孩她妈\N{\ren}Excuse me, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.15,1:41:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是汉莱提先生  我太太  卡罗尔\N{\ren}Honey, this is Mr. Handratty. My wife Carol.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.60,1:41:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 汉...   - 汉莱提  夫人\N{\ren}-Oh, Mister...? -Handratty, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.43,1:41:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 莱提  - 是的\N{\ren}-Ratty. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.24,1:41:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见弗兰克或布伦达了吗?\N{\ren}Have you seen Frank or Brenda?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.26,1:41:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他们上楼了\N{\ren}I-I think they went upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.00,1:41:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克...\N{\ren}Frank...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.43,1:41:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,布伦达  过来\N{\ren}Brenda, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.41,1:41:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,2天后  我们在...\N{\ren}Okay, in two days, you're going to meet me
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.20,1:41:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在迈阿密国际机场见面   好吗?\N{\ren}at Miami International Airport, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.32,1:41:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你父母睡觉后离开家\N{\ren}You're going to leave the house after your parents go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.50,1:41:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,搭出租车\N{\ren}You're going to take a taxicab.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.58,1:41:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,把这钱给出租司机\N{\ren}You give the taxi driver this money right here
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.87,1:41:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他整夜开\N{\ren}and you tell him to drive all through the night.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.52,1:41:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,布伦达  你将在上午10点离开\N{\ren}Brenda, you're going to leave at 10:00am.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.48,1:41:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- 上午10点  好吗?  - 但是...\N{\ren}- 10:00am, all right? - But...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.69,1:42:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那间屋子  先生?\N{\ren}Which room, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.24,1:42:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,拐角那间\N{\ren}In the corner.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.50,1:42:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说  好吗?\N{\ren}You have to listen to me, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.39,1:42:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,迈阿密国际机场到站口\N{\ren}The International Terminal in Miami, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.19,1:42:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 重复一遍  - 迈阿密国际机场到站口\N{\ren}- Say it. - Okay, the International Terminal in Miami.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.28,1:42:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不管怎样  - 不管怎样\N{\ren}-No matter what... - No matter what...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.06,1:42:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 搭出租车  - 我会的\N{\ren}-You're going to take a taxicab. - I will take a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.22,1:42:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,上午10点到那儿\N{\ren}You're going to be there at 10:00am.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.05,1:42:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我会到那儿的  不管怎样\N{\ren}I will be there at 10:00am, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.87,1:42:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 2天后  - 2天\N{\ren}-In two days. -Two days.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.10,1:42:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,2天  布伦达  2天\N{\ren}Two days, Brenda. Two days.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.74,1:42:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样两天后上午10点  我会到那儿\N{\ren}In two days, I'll be there no matter what, at 10:00am.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.34,1:42:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会告诉任何人\N{\ren}You're not going to tell anyone, Brenda.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.94,1:42:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,答应我\N{\ren}You have to promise me, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.13,1:42:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  求你!\N{\ren}Frank, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.52,1:42:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你走之前请告诉我你的名字\N{\ren}Before you go, please tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.94,1:42:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉我\N{\ren}Please, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.86,1:42:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,小弗兰克·威廉·阿巴戈内尔\N{\ren}Frank William Abagnale Jr.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.17,1:43:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,国际航班\N{\ren}National Airlines
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.66,1:43:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,27号班机  途径萨拉索塔  坦帕\N{\ren}flight number 27, serving Fort Myers, sarasota, Tampa
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.12,1:43:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,终点纽约肯尼迪机场  现在正在检票...\N{\ren}and New York Kennedy, is now available at gate n...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.88,1:43:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,14号通道\N{\ren}skycap, Gate 14. skycap, Gate 14.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.27,1:43:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,出租车!\N{\ren}Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.40,1:44:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,请您注意...\N{\ren}Your attention...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.50,1:45:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,布伦达\N{\ren}Brenda.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.58,1:45:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙没有出现  肯定是在耍咱们\N{\ren}This guy's a no-show. He must've got wise to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.76,1:45:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也许走漏了消息  今天不来明天也会来的\N{\ren}Maybe he was tipped. If he's not here today, he'll be tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.90,1:45:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,出国之前我们一定会抓到他.\N{\ren}We'll get him before he leaves the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.42,1:45:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有护照\N{\ren}He doesn't have a passport.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.86,1:45:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,过去的半年里他去过了哈佛和伯克利\N{\ren}For the last six months, he's gone to Harvard and Berkeley.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.40,1:45:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢打赌他已经弄到了护照\N{\ren}I'm betting he can get a passport.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.43,1:45:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们必须在迈阿密机场全神戒备\N{\ren}so we have all our men waiting for him here in Miami International.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.71,1:45:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这个机场他以前来过  了解这里的出口\N{\ren}He's used it before. He knows the layout.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.53,1:45:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经和迈阿密警方联系过他们会协助我们\N{\ren}I talked to Miami police; they've offered us
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.07,1:45:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,50名便衣警察会轮班盯防\N{\ren}50 uniformed cops in two shifts of 25.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.21,1:45:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的人现在在机场的已经有100多个了\N{\ren}With our guys, that's almost 100 men in one airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.41,1:45:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我们是不是应该通知其他地方?\N{\ren}Don't you think we should spread it around?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.27,1:45:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不  这里是他的逃离点\N{\ren}No, no, this is the exit point.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.92,1:45:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道他不会租一辆汽车\N{\ren}Well, how do you know he hasn't rented a car
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.38,1:45:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,然后跑到纽约或者亚特兰大的机场\N{\ren}and driven to airports in New York, Atlanta?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.67,1:45:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不在纽约  也不在亚特兰大\N{\ren}Because I'm not in New York. I'm not in Atlanta.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.37,1:45:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是弗兰克·罗伯茨\N{\ren}Yes, this is, uh, Frank Roberts
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.66,1:45:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我将在本地区的大学里巡回演讲\N{\ren}and I'm letting all the universities
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.47,1:46:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,来让大家了解到泛美航空的...\N{\ren}in the area know that Pan Am will be initiating
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.34,1:46:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,本年度最新的招聘计划\N{\ren}a new recruiting program this year.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.46,1:46:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,明早我将在贵校结束行程\N{\ren}I'II, uh, be stopping by your campus tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.81,1:46:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢你们的到来\N{\ren}Thank you all very much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.24,1:46:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,今天结束的时候\N{\ren}At the end of the day
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.47,1:46:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我将选择八名年轻女士...\N{\ren}I'll be choosing eight young ladies to be a part of...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.16,1:46:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,做为泛美未来的空中小姐\N{\ren}Pan Am's future stewardess flight crew program.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.82,1:46:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,同时这八位女士将陪同我\N{\ren}Now, these eight young ladies will accompany me
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.83,1:46:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,去欧洲进行两个月的巡回演讲\N{\ren}on a two-month public relations tour through Europe.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.32,1:46:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,途中她们将学习到\N{\ren}They will discover firsthand what it takes
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.06,1:46:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,如何成为泛美航空的一流空姐\N{\ren}to be a Pan American stewardess.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.15,1:46:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,给我最少两个兄弟...\N{\ren}Give me at least two men...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.79,1:46:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,两个通道最少要有一个人\N{\ren}Nah, one man per every two counters.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.37,1:46:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗\N{\ren}All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.58,1:46:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 阿姆德斯基?  - 嗯?\N{\ren}- Amdursky? - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.15,1:46:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,保证你的人  守着人行道和出入口\N{\ren}Make sure your uniforms are covering the sidewalk entrances and exits.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.67,1:46:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来经常巡查男洗手间\N{\ren}Hey... let's have, uh, periodic sweeps of the men's lav.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.86,1:46:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你  负责这里\N{\ren}You, here.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.64,1:46:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什么条件使我能成为未来的空中小姐?\N{\ren}What qualifies me to be a future stewardess?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.09,1:46:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我真的很友善\N{\ren}Well, I think that I'm really friendly
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.08,1:47:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真能帮助人...\N{\ren}and I can really help out
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.31,1:47:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,使人感到在飞机上受到欢迎  并且...\N{\ren}and, um, make people feel welcome on the plane and...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.15,1:47:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在90米的高度上\N{\ren}We'll be traveling at 6,000 miles per hour
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.39,1:47:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,以9600公里时速飞行\N{\ren}at an altitude of 300 feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.32,1:47:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我行装已打好  我准备好出发\N{\ren}All my bags are packed, I'm ready to go...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.54,1:47:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,依琳娜·安德森\N{\ren}Ilene Anderson.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.50,1:47:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,米姬·埃克\N{\ren}Miggy Acker.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.53,1:47:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,曼布拉·乔·麦克米伦\N{\ren}Debra Jo McMillan.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.40,1:47:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,坎迪·赫斯顿\N{\ren}Candy Heston.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.42,1:48:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见走在最前面的金发妞了吗?\N{\ren}You see that blonde out front?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.94,1:48:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我本该成为一名飞行员的  - 很对\N{\ren}- I should have been a pilot. - Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.66,1:48:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,汉莱提先生\N{\ren}Mr. Carl Handratty
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.43,1:48:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请接听免费电话\N{\ren}please pick up the courtesy telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.66,1:48:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,汉莱提\N{\ren}Handratty.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.27,1:48:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔  你的对讲机刚才不好使\N{\ren}Carl, your walkie-talkie wasn't working.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.17,1:48:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个穿泛美制服的人\N{\ren}There's a guy in a Pan Am uniform
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.69,1:48:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在大都市单排座车到站口J\N{\ren}sitting in a white Coupe DeVille out in front of Terminal J.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.00,1:48:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那是包机口\N{\ren}That's the charter terminal.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.57,1:48:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你看见他的脸了吗?\N{\ren}Can you get a look at his face?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.08,1:48:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他带着飞行员的帽子\N{\ren}He's got his pilot's cap on.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.44,1:49:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔  我想是他\N{\ren}Carl, I think it's him!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.35,1:49:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,从车里出来  弗兰克\N{\ren}Out of the car, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.60,1:49:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克?\N{\ren}Frank?!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.00,1:49:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,从车里出来\N{\ren}step out of the car!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.34,1:49:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,把手放在我能看见的地方别动\N{\ren}Keep your hands where I can see 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.16,1:49:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开枪  我只是个司机\N{\ren}Don't shoot me! I'm just a driver.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.98,1:49:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人给我100美元让我穿这制服...\N{\ren}A man paid me $100 to wear this uniform
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.10,1:49:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 到飞机场接人  - 你接谁?\N{\ren}- and pick someone up at the airport. - Who you picking up?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.70,1:49:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}接汉莱提
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.18,1:49:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,收队  我们走\N{\ren}Pack up, let's fly away.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.20,1:49:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}七个月后
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.90,1:49:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,南美洲  澳大利亚\N{\ren}South America, Australia
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.69,1:49:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,新加坡  埃及\N{\ren}Singapore, Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.67,1:49:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙完全失去疯了\N{\ren}The kid's gone completely out of control.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.81,1:50:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么没通知我?  - 谁也没通知  长官\N{\ren}- Why wasn't I called? - Nobody was called, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.88,1:50:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,银行直到上周才知道\N{\ren}The banks didn't know what was happening till last week.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:03.78,1:50:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\ren}That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.68,1:50:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没通知是因为这不是伪造\N{\ren}They didn't call 'cause it's not counterfeiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.38,1:50:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 反正是其他的事  - 到底是什么呢?\N{\ren}- It's something else. - Well, what is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.46,1:50:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他做的是真支票\N{\ren}He's making real checks, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.22,1:50:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,很完美...  航空公司辨别不出来\N{\ren}These are so perfect the airline didn't know the difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.94,1:50:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,上张支票是在一周前在马德里兑现的\N{\ren}Last check was cashed in Madrid a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.97,1:50:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜他还在那儿  我们现在就得出发\N{\ren}My guess is he's still there. We have to leave now, sir. Today.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.65,1:50:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪?  西班牙?  你想去西班牙?\N{\ren}Go where? Spain? You want to go to spain?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.32,1:50:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,最后他会回去的...  回到印支票的地方\N{\ren}Well, eventually, he's got to go back to where the checks were printed.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.63,1:50:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是他为什么在欧洲活动\N{\ren}I think that's why he's moving back through Europe.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.23,1:50:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,看着这地图  先生  他在做一个圈子\N{\ren}Look at the map, sir. He's making a circle.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.70,1:50:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他要用完支票了  我可能说得不准\N{\ren}He's running out of checks. I know it's a... it's a long shot, sir
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.01,1:50:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我们从马德里开始追踪他  \N{\ren}but if we track him from Madrid,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.92,1:50:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还是能抓住他的  - 如果你在这儿抓不住他\N{\ren}- sir, we could still catch him. - I'm sorry, Carl, if you couldn't catch him here
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.72,1:50:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那在别的地方也抓不住\N{\ren}you're not going to catch him there.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.97,1:50:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我们就让他跑掉吗\N{\ren}But, sir, we're going to let him get away.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.86,1:50:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔  是你让他跑掉的\N{\ren}No, Carl, you let him get away.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.38,1:51:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,完美的边界尺寸...  整个一圈\N{\ren}A perfect one-16th all the way around.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.50,1:51:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,上色毫无瑕疵\N{\ren}Color separation is flawless.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.40,1:51:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,墨迹没有流淌\N{\ren}There's no bleeding. Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.28,1:51:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在美国没有人能干得这么好\N{\ren}Nobody does work like this in the states.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.19,1:51:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我们\N{\ren}Nobody but us.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.49,1:51:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是在哪儿印制的?\N{\ren}Where was it printed?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.27,1:51:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是在一个老印刷机上  - 老印刷机\N{\ren}- It was printed on a monster... - A monster.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.17,1:51:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 海德尔堡  伊斯的利亚半岛  - 海德尔堡\N{\ren}- a Heidelberg, an Istra... - Heidelberg.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.81,1:51:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,过时的  4色的\N{\ren}a dinosaur, four colors.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.60,1:51:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,能感觉出印刷机的重量\N{\ren}You can smell the weight.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.20,1:51:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,2吨  不算墨水\N{\ren}Two tons, without the ink.
