Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.60,1:53:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 想尝一口吗?  - 但他们需要美国人的帮助\N{\ren}- You want a bite? - But they needed the help of an American.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.28,1:53:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你饿了吗?  想尝一口吗?\N{\ren}Are you hungry? You want a bite?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.11,1:53:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但我说了我不把他们带到你这里来\N{\ren}But I told them I wouldn't bring them to you
