Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.44,1:53:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没枪\N{\ren}No gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:56.00,1:53:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那你在跟我说什么?\N{\ren}And-and you're... and you're telling me what?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.49,1:54:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在外面有20多名法国警察?\N{\ren}there's two dozen French police officers out there
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.65,1:54:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就在平安夜?  你是那么说的吗?\N{\ren}right now on Christmas Eve? That's what you're telling me?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.69,1:54:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对  - 好吧  好吧\N{\ren}- Yeah. - All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:05.55,1:54:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这里没有窗户\N{\ren}Well, there's no windows here.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.19,1:54:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我到前门看看  - 不!  不!\N{\ren}- I'm going to take a look out the front door. - No! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.79,1:54:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉他们我先走出去给他们一个信号\N{\ren}I told them I'd walk out first and give a signal.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.77,1:54:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给  你自己戴上  - 不  我不戴\N{\ren}- Here, you can put these on yourself. - No, I can't do that! I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.96,1:54:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道为什么?\N{\ren}You know why?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:19.11,1:54:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你总是很蠢\N{\ren}'Cause I think you're full of shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:20.64,1:54:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我看外面一个人也没有\N{\ren}I don't... I don't think there's anyone else out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.17,1:54:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我看只有你和我\N{\ren}I think... I think it's just me and you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.69,1:54:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,对  只有你和我  你知道吗?\N{\ren}That's right. I think it's just me and you, and you know what?
