Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.55,1:54:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  很好\N{\ren}Ah, that's good. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:35.27,1:54:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你想让我看见什么\N{\ren}Tell me what you want me to see, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.55,1:54:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会对你撒谎的\N{\ren}I wouldn't lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.80,1:54:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你戴着结婚戒指\N{\ren}Look, you're wearing a wedding ring.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.68,1:54:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你戴着结婚戒指  卡尔!  这事你骗我了!\N{\ren}You're wearing a wedding ring, Carl! You lied to me about that!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.11,1:54:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是撒谎了?\N{\ren}Didn't you lie about that?!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.45,1:54:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你问我是不是有个家\N{\ren}You asked me if I had a family.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.19,1:54:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,过去有  但不再有了\N{\ren}I did, but I don't anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.68,1:54:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有问题吗?  不  没有问题\N{\ren}Yes? No, no, no, there is no problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.50,1:55:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们马上出来\N{\ren}We're coming out right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.00,1:55:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,干得不错  干得不错\N{\ren}Whoa, that was good. That was good.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.99,1:55:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是给旅馆前台服务员钱\N{\ren}What, did you... you pay some hotel desk clerk
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.71,1:55:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,让他给你打那个电话?  是你干的吧?\N{\ren}to make that call for you, is that what you did?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.22,1:55:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是卢克警官\N{\ren}It was Captain Luc.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.47,1:55:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有1分钟带你出去\N{\ren}I've got one minute to bring you out.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.02,1:55:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,卢克警官?  卢克警官!\N{\ren}Captain Luc? Captain Luc!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.78,1:55:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,卢克警官\N{\ren}Ooh, Captain Luc.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.77,1:55:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔  我得说  听起来很像那么回事\N{\ren}Well, Carl, I gotta say that-that sounds pretty official to me
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.43,1:55:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是像我说的...  我看只有...\N{\ren}but like I said, I... I think it's just
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.67,1:55:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你在这  只有我们俩\N{\ren}me and you here, it's me and you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.54,1:55:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你得来抓我\N{\ren}so you're going to have to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.71,1:55:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克  弗兰克  这件事你得相信我\N{\ren}Frank. Frank! You have to trust me on this!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.51,1:55:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人感到难堪  他们很生气\N{\ren}These people have been embarrassed, Frank. They're angry.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:27.90,1:55:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你抢了他们的银行  偷了他们的钱\N{\ren}You rob their banks, you steal their money
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.55,1:55:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,生活在他们的国家\N{\ren}you live in their country.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.54,1:55:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉过你会这样的\N{\ren}I told you this was what was going to happen
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.10,1:55:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没有其它了结方式\N{\ren}that there was no other way for it to end.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.71,1:55:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不要胡来\N{\ren}Don't make a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.96,1:55:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\ren}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.15,1:55:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  卡尔  你知道吗?\N{\ren}That's good, Carl, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.80,1:55:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,接着编\N{\ren}Keep pushing that lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.58,1:55:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,接着编直到编成真的\N{\ren}Keep pushing till you make it true.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.82,1:55:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会杀了你\N{\ren}They're going to kill you!
