Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.89,1:55:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的吗?\N{\ren}Is that the truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.81,1:56:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的\N{\ren}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.91,1:56:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你有孩子吗?  卡尔?\N{\ren}You have any children, Carl?
