Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.90,1:56:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你以女儿发誓?\N{\ren}You swear on your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.50,1:56:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你发誓?\N{\ren}You swear?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:25.00,1:56:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你发誓?\N{\ren}You swear?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.50,1:57:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了  卡尔\N{\ren}That was really good, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.59,1:57:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他由我监护\N{\ren}I have him in custody.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.85,1:57:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我控制住他了!\N{\ren}I got him.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.12,1:57:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我控制住他了!  没关系!\N{\ren}I got him! It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.25,1:57:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系!  我控制住他了!\N{\ren}It's all right! I got him!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.17,1:57:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我想做官方纪录\N{\ren}Hey, I want it... I want it on the record.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.67,1:57:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克·阿巴戈内尔自愿被捕\N{\ren}Frank Abagnale surrendered of his own accord.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.81,1:57:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗?  明白吗?\N{\ren}Understood? Understood?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.40,1:57:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要把他带哪里去?  我应该跟着\N{\ren}Where are you taking him? I'm... I'm supposed to go.
